1
00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:14,000
卢旺达饭店

2
00:00:15,280 --> 00:00:18,078
由于停火过晚 没能挽救这些村庄…
The latest ceasefire came too late to save these villages...

3
00:00:22,921 --> 00:00:25,754
今天克林顿总统表示将密切关注
Today President Clinton voiced concerns

4
00:00:25,754 --> 00:00:28,587
萨拉热窝日益恶化的局势…
at the deteriorating situation in Sarajevo...

5
00:00:33,399 --> 00:00:35,498
当人们问我 尊敬的听众朋友们
When people ask me, good listeners,

6
00:00:35,498 --> 00:00:37,597
为什么我讨厌所有的图西族人
why do I hate all the Tutsi,

7
00:00:37,669 --> 00:00:40,536
我说 “去看看我们的历史吧”
I say, "Read our history. "

8
00:00:40,606 --> 00:00:43,541
图西族曾通敌比利时殖民者
The Tutsi were collaborators for the Belgian colonists.

9
00:00:43,609 --> 00:00:46,601
他们强占我们胡图族的土地 用鞭子抽我们
They stole our Hutu land, they whipped us.

10
00:00:46,678 --> 00:00:49,772
现在这些图西族反叛分子 他们回来了
Now they have come back, these Tutsi rebels.

11
00:00:49,848 --> 00:00:53,113
他们如同蟑螂 他们是杀人犯
They are cockroaches. They are murderers.

12
00:00:53,185 --> 00:00:57,781
卢旺达是我们胡图族的领地 我们才是主人
Rwanda is our Hutu land. We are the majority.

13
00:00:57,856 --> 00:01:01,383
他们则是少数叛国者和侵略者
They are a minority of traitors and invaders.

14
00:01:01,460 --> 00:01:07,296
我们要粉碎他们的横行 消灭RPF反叛分子
We will squash the infestation. We will wipe out the RPF rebels.

15
00:01:07,366 --> 00:01:10,858
你收听的是RTLM（千丘广播电台）胡图族官方电台
This is RTLM, Hutu Power Radio.

16
00:01:10,936 --> 00:01:14,030
保持警惕 防范邻居
Stay alert. Watch your neighbors.

17
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:26,200
-=TLF字幕组=-
翻译：KOK
校对：KOK

18
00:01:26,500 --> 00:01:30,500
基加利（卢旺达首都） 1994

19
00:01:33,459 --> 00:01:36,951
- 卢斯赛伯吉纳先生 谢谢 - 见到你很高兴 先生
- Mr, Rusesabagina, thank you, - Good to see you, sir,

20
00:01:49,208 --> 00:01:50,197
谢谢
Thank you,

21
00:01:50,275 --> 00:01:52,675
这些事给你的 先生 刚从哈瓦那（古巴首都）带来的
These are for you, sir, They're fresh from Havana,

22
00:01:52,744 --> 00:01:55,736
太棒了 下次你去那儿代我向菲德尔问好
Wonderful, Next time you are there, tell Fidel that I said hello,

23
00:01:56,615 --> 00:01:57,946
先生们 很高兴见到你们
Good to see you gentlemen,

24
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:06,600
片名：卢旺达饭店

25
00:02:22,541 --> 00:02:25,101
那是支上等的雪茄 先生
That is a fine cigar, sir,

26
00:02:25,777 --> 00:02:27,506
这是Cohiba牌的雪茄（注：Cohiba是世界顶级雪茄烟品牌）
This is a Cohiba cigar,

27
00:02:27,579 --> 00:02:31,515
- 每一支值10,000法郎 - 10,000法郎？
- Each one is worth 10,000 francs, - 10,000 francs?

28
00:02:31,583 --> 00:02:34,882
是的 不错 但对我来说比10,000法郎还值钱
Yes, yes, But it is worth more to me than 10,000 francs,

29
00:02:34,953 --> 00:02:36,580
怎么讲 先生？
What do you mean, sir?

30
00:02:39,291 --> 00:02:43,387
要是给一个商人10,000法郎 这对他来说意味着什么？
If I give a businessman 10,000 francs, what does that matter to him?

31
00:02:43,462 --> 00:02:47,398
他不缺钱的 但是…如果我给他一支Cohiba牌的雪茄
He is rich, But if I give him a Cohiba cigar

32
00:02:47,466 --> 00:02:52,165
直接从古巴首都哈瓦那带回来的…嘿 这就体面了 杜比
straight from Havana, Cuba,,, Hey, that is style, Dube,

33
00:02:52,938 --> 00:02:54,030
是蛮体面
Style,

34
00:03:03,982 --> 00:03:06,974
Cohiba――不可思议的雪茄
Cohiba--a fantastic cigar,

35
00:03:07,886 --> 00:03:09,183
是最好的 对吧？
The best, eh?

36
00:03:09,254 --> 00:03:11,916
那今天的集会 你会来参加吧？
So, you're going to join us at the rally today?

37
00:03:14,493 --> 00:03:15,824
我会尽力而为 乔治
I will try my best, George,

38
00:03:15,894 --> 00:03:19,489
这些日子我没时间参加集会和政治活动
but these days I have no time for rallies and politics,

39
00:03:19,565 --> 00:03:22,966
政治就是权势 保罗 胡图族的权势
Politics is power, Paul, Hutu power,

40
00:03:23,035 --> 00:03:24,400
以及财富
And money,

41
00:03:28,740 --> 00:03:30,901
现在是你加入的时候了
It's time for you to join your people,

42
00:03:32,444 --> 00:03:33,741
谢谢 乔治
Thank you, George,

43
00:03:34,613 --> 00:03:36,604
但是时间也是金钱
But time is also money,

44
00:03:37,950 --> 00:03:40,783
今天我要在常规订单的基础上
I need six extra cases of beer today,

45
00:03:40,852 --> 00:03:42,683
再加六箱啤酒
along with the regular order,

46
00:03:45,824 --> 00:03:48,486
- 饭店生意很好嘛 - 非常好
- Business is good at the hotel, - It is very good,

47
00:03:49,428 --> 00:03:51,692
见到你总是很高兴 保罗
I'm always glad to see you, Paul,

48
00:03:58,437 --> 00:04:01,031
放回去！放回去！那不是啤酒！
Put that back! Put that back! That's not beer!

49
00:04:06,378 --> 00:04:08,869
- 你 来收拾一下 - 好的 先生 来
- You, clean this up, - Yes, sir, Come on,

50
00:04:08,947 --> 00:04:11,643
保罗 嘉士伯牌的没了 但别担心
Paul, don't worry about the Carlsberg,

51
00:04:11,717 --> 00:04:14,481
我会给你喜力牌的 我不向你额外收费
I'll give you Heineken, and I won't charge you extra,

52
00:04:14,553 --> 00:04:15,542
谢谢
Thank you,

53
00:04:20,025 --> 00:04:23,620
从中国买的便宜货――每把十分钱
A bargain buy from China-- ten cents each,

54
00:04:24,663 --> 00:04:27,063
知道吗 我至少能卖五十分
You know, I'll get at least fifty,

55
00:04:27,733 --> 00:04:29,030
至少
At least,

56
00:04:36,441 --> 00:04:39,001
乔治・卢塔甘达是个坏人
George Rutaganda is a bad man,

57
00:04:39,077 --> 00:04:41,910
我在广播上听到 他叫胡图族屠杀所有图西族人
I've heard him on the radio telling the Hutus to kill all the Tutsis,

58
00:04:43,348 --> 00:04:46,408
卢塔甘达那帮人 都是白痴 杜比
Rutaganda and his people, they are fools, Dube,

59
00:04:46,485 --> 00:04:48,749
他们的好景到头了
Their time is soon over,

60
00:04:48,820 --> 00:04:50,788
不管怎样 这是谈生意
Anyway, this is business,

61
00:04:56,762 --> 00:05:00,391
- 噢 不 是部族民兵 - 按他们说的做 靠边
- Oh, no, It's the lnterhamwe, - Do as they say, Pull over,

62
00:05:20,585 --> 00:05:22,644
别 别 坐直 杜比 坐直
No, no, sit up, Dube, Sit up,

63
00:05:22,721 --> 00:05:24,712
带点笑容 杜比 别引人注目
Smile, Dube, Don't attract attention to yourself,

64
00:05:24,790 --> 00:05:28,692
这些人有的是我邻居 他们知道我是图西族人
Some of these men are my neighbors, They know that I'm Tutsi,

65
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:31,285
稍微笑笑 就好像大家都是朋友 杜比
Just smile as if they are friends, Dube,

66
00:05:35,801 --> 00:05:38,599
- 我认识这个人！ - 你是图西族人？
- I know this man! - Are you a Tutsi?

67
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:40,001
你在这儿干什么？
What are you doing here?

68
00:05:40,072 --> 00:05:43,769
不 不 胡图族势力 胡图族势力 胡图族势力！
No, no, Hutu power, Hutu power, Hutu power!

69
00:05:45,210 --> 00:05:46,939
好 是的！
Okay, Yes!

70
00:05:51,249 --> 00:05:52,580
离开这儿
Get out of here,

71
00:06:00,892 --> 00:06:02,883
箱子里有水渗出
There's water coming from the box,

72
00:06:02,961 --> 00:06:05,122
停在这儿 我们从前面走
Park here, We'll go in the front,

73
00:06:08,567 --> 00:06:10,797
格莱戈瓦 请帮忙把水拖一下
Gregoire, please help with this water,

74
00:06:12,003 --> 00:06:13,300
格莱戈瓦！
Gregoire!

75
00:06:13,372 --> 00:06:14,999
马上来拖
Deal with this right away,

76
00:06:15,073 --> 00:06:16,637
我们希望看到歹徒
We were hoping to go see the gorilla.

77
00:06:16,637 --> 00:06:18,201
你应该和我们旅行队联系一下
You must contact our safari desk,

78
00:06:19,811 --> 00:06:22,143
杜比 这儿是大厅
Dube, this is the lobby,

79
00:06:22,214 --> 00:06:24,842
- 怎么回事？ - 抱歉 先生 紧急情况
- What's going on? - I am sorry, sir, It is an emergency,

80
00:06:28,653 --> 00:06:30,883
- 噢 见鬼！ - 噢 抱歉 先生
Oh, shit! Oh, sorry, sir,

81
00:06:34,393 --> 00:06:36,486
十只活的 十二只死的
Ten alive, twelve are dead,

82
00:06:39,030 --> 00:06:40,190
不要紧
All right,

83
00:06:41,166 --> 00:06:42,997
把壳留着
But save the shells,

84
00:06:43,068 --> 00:06:44,558
用东西…
Fill them with,,,

85
00:06:45,504 --> 00:06:48,667
…填满 用精肉和当地的一些食物
,,,a stuffing, The good meat and something local,

86
00:06:48,740 --> 00:06:52,506
- 木薯行吗？ - 还有…鱼肉
- Cassava? - And,,,the fish,

87
00:06:52,577 --> 00:06:54,772
- 还有面包皮 - 是的
- And tipali, - Yes,

88
00:06:54,846 --> 00:06:58,612
就叫作“木薯面包鲜龙虾”
We'll call it "fresh lobster in a cassava and tipali crust,"

89
00:06:58,683 --> 00:06:59,672
杜比
Dube,

90
00:06:59,751 --> 00:07:01,150
够体面 先生
Style, sir,

91
00:07:01,219 --> 00:07:02,686
是的 先生
Yes, sir,

92
00:07:05,524 --> 00:07:09,620
比齐蒙戈将军 问题在于 我得知
The problem is, General Bizimungu, I have information

93
00:07:09,694 --> 00:07:14,893
部族民兵不会接受和平协定
that the lnterhamwe militia will not heed the peace agreement,

94
00:07:14,966 --> 00:07:18,527
上校 联合国 不必担心部族的问题
Colonel, the U,N, need not worry about the lnterhamwe,

95
00:07:18,603 --> 00:07:19,831
我们能有效控制他们
We will control them,

96
00:07:19,905 --> 00:07:22,066
- 将军 - 保罗
- General, - Paul,

97
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:24,233
这瓶苏格兰威士忌不同寻常
This scotch is exceptional,

98
00:07:24,309 --> 00:07:28,075
这是我们最受欢迎的单一麦芽威士忌 我知道你会喜欢的
It is our most popular single malt, I knew you'd like it,

99
00:07:28,146 --> 00:07:30,011
奥利弗上校 很荣幸见到您 先生
Colonel Oliver, it is a pleasure to see you, sir,

100
00:07:30,081 --> 00:07:32,072
见到你很高兴 保罗
Good to see you, Paul,

101
00:07:32,684 --> 00:07:35,676
将军 我来介绍一下今天的龙虾
General, let me recommend the lobster for lunch today,

102
00:07:35,754 --> 00:07:37,722
是精心准备的――空运来的
It is spectacular-- straight off the plane,

103
00:07:37,789 --> 00:07:40,690
基加利鲜龙虾 你让我们感到自豪 保罗
Fresh lobster in Kigali, You do us proud, Paul,

104
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:41,748
谢谢
Thank you,

105
00:07:41,827 --> 00:07:44,728
在存衣处 我也给你留了点
I left a little something for you at the coat check,

106
00:07:45,831 --> 00:07:47,230
抱歉 先生们
Excuse me, gentlemen,

107
00:07:49,401 --> 00:07:51,631
还需要面粉 给我两袋面粉
I need flour, Give me two bags of flour,

108
00:07:53,171 --> 00:07:55,264
好了 开饭了 来啦
Okay, the plates are ready, Here they come,

109
00:07:57,709 --> 00:07:59,370
下午好 女士们
Good afternoon, ladies,

110
00:07:59,444 --> 00:08:02,004
伊丽莎白 拜托把这个放到将军的衣箱里
Elizabeth, please put these in the general's briefcase,

111
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:03,377
好的 先生
Yes, sir,

112
00:08:05,183 --> 00:08:06,775
这是RTLM（千丘广播电台） 胡图族官方电台
This is RTLM, Hutu Power Radio.

113
00:08:07,352 --> 00:08:10,150
我要带给总统先生一个消息
I have a message for our president.

114
00:08:10,222 --> 00:08:14,124
警惕 别相信图西族反叛分子
Beware. Do not trust the Tutsi rebels.

115
00:08:14,192 --> 00:08:16,717
别和他们握手 他们会杀了你
Do not shake the hand that will stab you.

116
00:08:16,795 --> 00:08:18,057
他们对待你会像…
They will treat you...

117
00:08:18,964 --> 00:08:21,899
…来自卢旺达首都基加利的报道 这里气氛高度紧张
... reporting from Kigali, Rwanda, where tensions are high

118
00:08:21,967 --> 00:08:25,130
由于签署联合国和平条约的最后期限正在逼近
as the deadline for the U. N.-brokered peace agreement approaches.

119
00:08:29,641 --> 00:08:30,938
你好啊 保罗先生
Hello, Mr, Paul,

120
00:08:44,589 --> 00:08:46,147
你好 耶利米
Hello, Jeremiah,

121
00:08:46,658 --> 00:08:47,818
你好 先生
Hello, sir,

122
00:08:53,231 --> 00:08:55,290
- 很高兴见到你 保罗 - 奥德特
- Good to see you, Paul, - Odette,

123
00:08:57,035 --> 00:08:58,525
回头见
See you soon,

124
00:09:00,505 --> 00:09:02,564
你弟弟和女孩们都在这儿
So your brother and the girls are here,

125
00:09:02,641 --> 00:09:03,835
是的
Yes,

126
00:09:05,043 --> 00:09:06,067
一、二、三…
One, two, three,,,

127
00:09:06,144 --> 00:09:08,009
噢 卡琳！
Oh, Carine!

128
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,648
好 爱耐丝 我看看 轮到你了
Okay, Anais, let me see, Your turn,

129
00:09:10,715 --> 00:09:12,148
一、二、三…
One, two, three,,,

130
00:09:14,352 --> 00:09:17,116
- 谁赢了？ - 噢 这不重要
Who is the winner? Oh, it doesn't matter,

131
00:09:17,188 --> 00:09:18,951
我带了巧克力 谁要巧克力？
I have chocolates, Who wants chocolates?

132
00:09:19,024 --> 00:09:20,150
嗨 爸爸 看这个
Hey, Papa, watch this,

133
00:09:23,428 --> 00:09:26,625
噢 天哪 呃 这儿 巧克力 巧克力 谁想要？
Oh, my goodness, Well, here, chocolates, chocolates, Who wants?

134
00:09:27,198 --> 00:09:29,393
给保罗叔叔说谢谢
Say thank you to your Uncle Paul,

135
00:09:29,467 --> 00:09:32,561
- 拜托 别在饭前吃 - 别在饭前吃哦 你妈妈说了
- Please, not before dinner, - Not before dinner, Mama says,

136
00:09:32,637 --> 00:09:34,764
- 谢谢 - 好的 好的
- Thank you, - Okay, okay,

137
00:09:34,839 --> 00:09:36,101
我们进去
Let's go in,

138
00:09:42,347 --> 00:09:45,510
商店的生意不景气 饭店情况怎么样？
Things are very slow at the shop, How are things at the hotel?

139
00:09:45,584 --> 00:09:48,747
很忙 很多人来看暴徒
Very busy, Many people visiting the gorillas,

140
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:51,618
很多外国记者为和平协定而来…
A lot of foreign press arriving for the peace acc--

141
00:09:51,690 --> 00:09:54,215
- 怎么了？ - 有士兵
- What? - There are soldiers,

142
00:09:54,292 --> 00:09:56,852
- 哪儿？ - 就在路上
- Where? - On the street,

143
00:10:00,932 --> 00:10:03,765
我去看看怎么回事 没事儿
I'll go see what's happening, It's all right,

144
00:10:06,671 --> 00:10:10,664
- 我们知道你是图西族的 - 求求你了 先生 他是我丈夫
- We know you are Tutsi, - Please, sir, this is my husband,

145
00:10:10,742 --> 00:10:13,142
- 他只是个园丁 - 他替反叛分子当间谍
- He's just a gardener, - He's been spying for the rebels,

146
00:10:13,211 --> 00:10:15,975
- 不 我们不认识反叛分子 - 你跟我们走！
- No, we do not know any rebels, - You will come with us!

147
00:10:16,047 --> 00:10:19,073
不 我们说的都是实话 我们不认识…
No, we are telling the truth, We do not know any,,,

148
00:10:19,951 --> 00:10:21,384
- 怎么了？ - 别出声！
- What is it? - Shut up!

149
00:10:21,453 --> 00:10:24,115
塔莎娜 回屋里去 你快回去
Tatiana, go back in the house, You must go back,

150
00:10:24,189 --> 00:10:26,157
- 你别出来 - 是维克托
- You mustn't be out here, - It's Victor,

151
00:10:29,027 --> 00:10:31,086
别 上校 你看…
No, Captain, you see--

152
00:10:31,162 --> 00:10:34,290
不是我 不是我 上校 上校
It's not me, It's not me, Captain, Captain,

153
00:10:34,366 --> 00:10:36,926
为什么带他走？求求你了 求求你了
Why are you taking him away? Please, please,

154
00:10:37,002 --> 00:10:39,436
- 我知道 我知道 但不是我干的 - 你们这帮图西族白痴
- I know, I know, but it's not me, - You Tutsi fuckers,

155
00:10:40,605 --> 00:10:42,072
不！不！
No! No!

156
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:43,471
我们得想想办法
We must do something,

157
00:10:43,541 --> 00:10:45,236
- 想什么办法？ - 叫人
- Do what? - Call someone,

158
00:10:45,310 --> 00:10:48,211
我不去 我不去
I'm not going, I'm not going,

159
00:10:48,279 --> 00:10:49,303
别！
No!

160
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,515
带到车上去 马上！
Get him in the truck, Now!

161
00:10:58,623 --> 00:11:00,318
我们得想想办法
We must do something,

162
00:11:00,392 --> 00:11:02,451
求求你帮帮他！
Please help him!

163
00:11:02,527 --> 00:11:04,961
噢 维克托！
Oh, Victor!

164
00:11:05,530 --> 00:11:06,519
维克托！
Victor!

165
00:11:06,598 --> 00:11:08,463
我们无能为力
There is nothing we can do,

166
00:11:09,501 --> 00:11:12,334
- 你今晚不能走 托马斯 - 好的
- You must stay the night, Thomas, - Yes,

167
00:11:15,306 --> 00:11:17,137
不！
No!

168
00:11:18,977 --> 00:11:21,036
他们为什么抓维克托？
Why would they arrest Victor?

169
00:11:23,281 --> 00:11:25,146
他没从事过政治活动啊
He has no politics,

170
00:11:25,984 --> 00:11:28,748
- 他是园丁 - 谁知道 塔莎？
- He's a gardener, - Who knows, Tatsi?

171
00:11:29,921 --> 00:11:31,081
谁知道？
Who knows?

172
00:11:31,656 --> 00:11:35,057
有人看不惯他 就说他替反叛分子当间谍
Someone who didn't like him denounced him as a rebel spy,

173
00:11:36,394 --> 00:11:38,123
一直有这种事发生
Happens all the time now,

174
00:11:40,065 --> 00:11:45,093
或许你可以联系一下军队里的熟人
Maybe you could call one of your contacts in the army,

175
00:11:45,837 --> 00:11:47,361
没用的
It wouldn't help,

176
00:11:48,973 --> 00:11:50,770
你可以让他帮帮忙
You could ask as a favor,

177
00:11:50,842 --> 00:11:53,003
不 我不
No, I could not,

178
00:11:54,345 --> 00:11:59,146
塔莎 我整天都在取悦于这个军官、
Tatsi, all day long I work to please this officer,

179
00:11:59,217 --> 00:12:03,085
那个外交官、一些旅游的人 就是为了得到他们的支持
that diplomat, some tourist, to store up favors

180
00:12:03,154 --> 00:12:05,782
要是当“我们”需要帮助时
so if there is a time when we need help,

181
00:12:05,857 --> 00:12:07,916
我能找到能起作用的人
I have powerful people I can call upon,

182
00:12:07,992 --> 00:12:10,324
可维克托是个好邻居啊
But Victor was a good neighbor,

183
00:12:10,395 --> 00:12:14,695
他不是我的家人 家人才是至关重要的
He is not family, Family is all that matters,

184
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:20,565
拜托 拜托 这件事就按我说的办
Please, please, leave these things to my good judgment,

185
00:12:36,354 --> 00:12:38,686
这个安排简直是胡扯
This assignment is bullshit,

186
00:12:38,757 --> 00:12:41,817
拜托 在上等饭店呆着就没人能伤害我们了？
Come on, A few days in a nice hotel, no one shooting at us?

187
00:12:44,095 --> 00:12:47,496
先生们 欢迎光临米尔・科林斯饭店
Gentlemen, welcome to the Mille Collines,

188
00:12:47,565 --> 00:12:49,795
我是保罗・卢斯赛伯吉纳 客房经理
I am Paul Rusesabagina, the house manager,

189
00:12:49,868 --> 00:12:51,699
- 你好吗？ - 很高兴见到您
- How you doing? - Nice to meet you,

190
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:53,965
有任何需要 和我说便是
Anything that you need, please find me,

191
00:12:54,038 --> 00:12:55,403
- 谢谢 - 当然的
- Thank you, - Certainly,

192
00:13:02,981 --> 00:13:07,042
那胡图族人和图西族人有什么区别？
So, what is the actual difference between a Hutu and a Tutsi?

193
00:13:07,118 --> 00:13:09,319
按照比利时殖民者的说法
According to the Belgian colonists, 

194
00:13:09,319 --> 00:13:11,521
图西族人更高 且举止更为优雅
the Tutsis are taller and more elegant,

195
00:13:11,589 --> 00:13:14,558
是比利时人区分的
It was the Belgians that created the division,

196
00:13:14,626 --> 00:13:16,116
怎么讲？
How?

197
00:13:16,194 --> 00:13:19,527
他们把鼻子较窄的、皮肤较白的人挑出来
They picked people, those with thinner noses, lighter skin,

198
00:13:19,597 --> 00:13:21,656
他们曾经测量所有人鼻子的宽度
They used to measure the width of people's noses,

199
00:13:21,733 --> 00:13:24,258
比利时人利用图西族人来统治国家
The Belgians used the Tutsis to run the country,

200
00:13:24,335 --> 00:13:26,667
他们离开后 又把政权交给了胡图族人
Then when they left, they left the power to the Hutus,

201
00:13:26,738 --> 00:13:29,002
当然胡图族人由于被镇压多年
and of course the Hutus took revenge

202
00:13:29,073 --> 00:13:31,337
便对图西族的政界要人采取了报复行为
on the elite Tutsis for years of repression,

203
00:13:31,409 --> 00:13:33,206
我说的对吗 保罗？
Am I telling the truth, Paul?

204
00:13:33,278 --> 00:13:36,611
是的 很不幸的遭遇 请把这个给将军
Yes, unfortunately, Please take this to the general,

205
00:13:37,782 --> 00:13:40,979
本尼迪克特是基加利最好的记者 这方面的专家
Benedict is our finest journalist in Kigali, an expert on the subject,

206
00:13:42,687 --> 00:13:44,052
那你是哪个族的 保罗？
So what are you, Paul?

207
00:13:46,724 --> 00:13:47,952
我是胡图族
I am Hutu,

208
00:13:48,860 --> 00:13:50,020
先生们
Gentlemen,

209
00:13:50,094 --> 00:13:54,656
- 再来点香槟？ - 很不错 再来点香槟吧
- More champagne? - More champagne would be nice,

210
00:13:54,732 --> 00:13:58,031
抱歉 宝贝 能问个私人问题吗？
Excuse me, honey, Can I ask you a personal question?

211
00:13:58,102 --> 00:14:02,539
- 你是胡图族还是图西族？ - 我是图西族
- Are you a Hutu or a Tutsi? - I am Tutsi,

212
00:14:02,607 --> 00:14:06,441
- 你朋友呢？也是图西族？ - 不 我是胡图族
- And your friend? Tutsi? - No, I am Hutu,

213
00:14:09,180 --> 00:14:10,511
还能是双胞胎
They could be twins,

214
00:14:11,082 --> 00:14:14,245
去拿摄像机 将军要接见我们
Get the camera, The general's going to give us an interview,

215
00:14:14,319 --> 00:14:15,308
好的
Okay,

216
00:14:16,688 --> 00:14:20,590
我住22号房 我想和你继续聊聊
I'm in room 22, I'd love to finish up this conversation,

217
00:14:23,461 --> 00:14:27,557
联合国高级军官声称卢旺达秘密组织了武装力量
Senior U.N. officers claim that the Rwandan army is secretly training

218
00:14:27,632 --> 00:14:30,897
将胡图族民兵装备为部落民兵
and arming the Hutu militia called the Interhamwe.

219
00:14:30,969 --> 00:14:35,406
就这项声明 我采访了武装力量的领袖比齐蒙戈将军
I put this claim to the head of the armed forces, General Bizimungu.

220
00:14:35,473 --> 00:14:39,170
不 不 我们从未训练民兵
No. No, we have not been training the militia.

221
00:14:39,244 --> 00:14:41,235
联合国对此表示指责是错误的
The U. N. are mistaken in this accusation.

222
00:14:41,312 --> 00:14:43,906
你赞成总统和反叛分子签署和平协定吗？
Do you support your president's agreement to make peace with the rebels?

223
00:14:43,982 --> 00:14:47,440
全军上下都支持总统的决定
The president has the full support of the army.

224
00:14:47,518 --> 00:14:50,510
图西族叛军和哈比亚利马纳总统
That peace agreement will be signed today in Tanzania

225
00:14:50,588 --> 00:14:53,955
将于今天在坦桑尼亚签署和平协定
between Tutsi rebel forces and President Habyarimana.

226
00:14:54,025 --> 00:14:56,823
对于卢旺达 对于整个非洲来说
This is a great day for Rwanda

227
00:14:56,895 --> 00:14:58,829
都是不寻常的一天
and for all of Africa,

228
00:14:58,897 --> 00:15:01,559
谈判取代了双方的对峙状态
Negotiation has replaced confrontation,,,

229
00:15:01,633 --> 00:15:04,101
保罗 来喝一杯
Paul, have a drink,

230
00:15:04,168 --> 00:15:05,999
友谊取代了恐慌
Friendship has replaced fear,

231
00:15:06,070 --> 00:15:08,334
女士们先生们 我们为和平协定的签署
Ladies and gentlemen, we have a live feed

232
00:15:08,406 --> 00:15:10,271
准备了丰盛的午餐
to the signing of the peace agreement,

233
00:15:10,341 --> 00:15:13,799
为我们的总统先生干杯 希望他能重现和平
To our president, May he find peace,

234
00:15:14,812 --> 00:15:16,541
希望所有人都和平共处
May we all find peace,

235
00:15:16,614 --> 00:15:22,314
愿我们大家都致力于维护这来之不易的协定
Let us all dedicate ourselves to nurturing this hard-earned accord,

236
00:15:22,387 --> 00:15:23,649
为和平干杯！
To peace!

237
00:15:23,721 --> 00:15:24,847
为和平干杯！
Peace!

238
00:15:27,058 --> 00:15:28,758
你来的话 别忘了来我这儿
Look me up if you come over,

239
00:15:28,758 --> 00:15:30,459
好的 这是个美丽的城市
Yes, it is a beautiful city,

240
00:15:30,528 --> 00:15:33,053
我正打算回去――真抱歉
I am planning on returning there as-- Forgive me,

241
00:15:33,131 --> 00:15:35,224
- 谢谢 拜 - 托马斯
- Thank you, Bye, - Thomas,

242
00:15:37,468 --> 00:15:39,333
- 你好 费登丝 - 保罗
- Hello, Fedens, - Paul,

243
00:15:39,904 --> 00:15:41,599
呃 这真让人吃惊
Well, this is a surprise,

244
00:15:41,673 --> 00:15:44,073
抱歉 保罗 我们得谈谈
Forgive us, Paul, We must talk,

245
00:15:44,943 --> 00:15:46,911
好啊 怎么了？
Yes, what's wrong?

246
00:15:46,978 --> 00:15:49,811
据可靠消息称 保罗
I have it from a very reliable source, Paul,

247
00:15:49,881 --> 00:15:51,007
谁？
Who?

248
00:15:52,450 --> 00:15:53,917
谢谢 萨利文
Thank you, Sullivan,

249
00:15:55,820 --> 00:15:59,586
我的助手 胡图族的人
My assistant, the Hutu Power man,

250
00:15:59,657 --> 00:16:02,717
他说我们必须立刻离开这儿 形势马上就会变得很糟糕
He says that we must get out now, that soon it'll be very bad,

251
00:16:03,895 --> 00:16:05,328
这人叫什么名字
Give me this man's name,

252
00:16:05,396 --> 00:16:08,991
拜托 保罗 尽管他是部族民兵 但他是朋友
Please, Paul, even though he is lnterhamwe, he's a friend,

253
00:16:09,067 --> 00:16:10,864
他是想要你的工作 托马斯
He wants your job, Thomas,

254
00:16:14,906 --> 00:16:18,137
他说有个信号
He said that there is a signal,

255
00:16:19,310 --> 00:16:21,835
即“砍掉高的树木”
It is "Cut the tall trees,"

256
00:16:22,680 --> 00:16:25,672
一旦听到这个讯号 民兵就会投入战斗
And when they hear this signal, the militia are to go to war,

257
00:16:25,750 --> 00:16:29,686
保罗 求求你了 让塔莎娜和我们走吧
Paul, please, let us take Tatiana with us,

258
00:16:29,754 --> 00:16:31,722
你是胡图族 你会很安全的
You are Hutu, You will be safe,

259
00:16:32,924 --> 00:16:36,826
费登丝 我知道你听到了很多传言
Fedens, I know you have heard many things,

260
00:16:37,795 --> 00:16:39,786
我也知道我们看到的状况 托马斯
And I know what we have seen, Thomas,

261
00:16:39,864 --> 00:16:42,594
但是拜托 联合国的人现在在这儿
But please, the United Nations are here now,

262
00:16:42,667 --> 00:16:45,227
世界各地的记者都保持着关注
The world press are watching,

263
00:16:45,303 --> 00:16:48,136
和平协定也都签署了 这个进程…
The peace has been signed, Let this process work--

264
00:16:48,206 --> 00:16:49,764
怎么了？
What was that?

265
00:16:54,012 --> 00:16:55,343
停电了
Power cuts,

266
00:16:56,647 --> 00:16:58,842
我们会自行发电的
We are running on generators,

267
00:16:59,851 --> 00:17:01,785
费登丝…
Fedens,,,

268
00:17:01,853 --> 00:17:03,480
拜托 别担心
Please, don't worry,

269
00:17:05,456 --> 00:17:07,424
明天你过来
Tomorrow you will come by the house

270
00:17:07,424 --> 00:17:09,392
我们和塔莎娜商量一下
and we will discuss this with Tatiana,

271
00:17:09,460 --> 00:17:10,791
好吗？
All right?

272
00:17:13,431 --> 00:17:16,491
- 晚安 保罗 - 是的 代我吻吻姑娘们
- Good night, Paul, - Yes, Kiss the girls for me,

273
00:17:44,996 --> 00:17:46,293
见鬼！
Shit!

274
00:18:00,445 --> 00:18:03,414
呆在家里别出来 呆在家里别出来
Stay in your houses, Stay in your house,

275
00:18:03,481 --> 00:18:05,608
所有人都呆在家里别出来！
Everybody stay in your house!

276
00:18:37,281 --> 00:18:38,441
塔莎娜？
Tatiana?

277
00:19:08,346 --> 00:19:10,541
- 保罗！ - 塔莎娜！
- Paul! - Tatiana!

278
00:19:12,150 --> 00:19:14,812
- 这儿怎么回事？ - 我们的房子被烧了
- What is going on here? - Our house has been burned,

279
00:19:15,353 --> 00:19:17,719
- 你没听到新闻？ - 什么新闻？
- Didn't you hear the news? - What news?

280
00:19:17,788 --> 00:19:21,087
据说哈比亚利马纳总统被谋杀了
They are saying President Habyarimana has been murdered,

281
00:19:21,159 --> 00:19:22,956
图西族反叛分子干的
Tutsi rebels have killed him,

282
00:19:23,027 --> 00:19:26,485
瞎说 总统是去签署和平协定的 怎么会被反叛分子谋杀？
Nonsense, Why would the rebels kill the president when he agreed to peace?

283
00:19:29,767 --> 00:19:32,497
各位 拜托 别呆在这儿 拜托
Everyone, please, out of this room, Please,

284
00:19:32,570 --> 00:19:34,561
吉恩・巴提斯 让他们到别的房间去坐
Jean Baptiste, find them seats in the other room,

285
00:19:34,639 --> 00:19:36,436
奥德特 拜托
Odette, please,

286
00:19:39,810 --> 00:19:43,940
- 你见到托马斯和费登丝了？ - 不错 我让他们回家去
- Did you meet with Thomas and Fedens? - Yes, I told them to go home,

287
00:19:44,949 --> 00:19:48,510
- 去给他们打个电话 塔莎 - 我试过了 电话…不能用
- Go and call them, Tatsi, - I've tried, Our phones, they do not work,

288
00:19:52,924 --> 00:19:54,903
为什么邻居都跑到我们家来？
Why do the neighbors run to us?

289
00:19:54,903 --> 00:19:56,883
你是他们唯一能信任的胡图族人
You are the only Hutu they can trust,

290
00:19:56,961 --> 00:19:58,553
但你是图西族啊
You are a Tutsi,

291
00:19:58,629 --> 00:20:01,928
他们很害怕 保罗 我也很害怕
They are scared, Paul, I am scared,

292
00:20:08,239 --> 00:20:11,072
这可能是煽动者放出的谣言
These are probably rumors started by agitators,

293
00:20:11,142 --> 00:20:13,975
为了孩子们 我们必须保持平静 塔莎 我们必须这样
We must remain calm for the children, Tatsi, We must,

294
00:20:14,478 --> 00:20:18,005
抱歉 保罗 伊利说罗杰走了
Forgive me, Paul, Elys says that Roger has gone,

295
00:20:18,082 --> 00:20:20,346
走了？去哪儿了？
Gone? Gone where?

296
00:20:20,418 --> 00:20:24,115
- 他担心他的朋友西蒙 妈妈 - 他去哪儿了 伊利？
- He was afraid for his friend Simon, Mama, - Where has he gone, Elys?

297
00:20:24,188 --> 00:20:25,314
去隔壁了
He went next door,

298
00:20:26,224 --> 00:20:28,055
等等 保罗！
Wait, Paul!

299
00:20:28,125 --> 00:20:31,151
塔莎娜 别来 你去和孩子们呆着
Tatiana, no, You have to stay here with the children,

300
00:20:31,229 --> 00:20:33,129
- 到屋里去 别出来！ - 拜托
- Stay in the house, No! - Please,

301
00:20:41,005 --> 00:20:44,497
保罗 拜托 怎么了？给我说 怎么了？
Paul, please, what is wrong? Tell me, what is wrong?

302
00:20:44,575 --> 00:20:47,544
- 噢 儿子！你哪儿受伤了？ - 他还好吗？噢 宝贝！
- Oh, my son! Where are you hurt? - Is he okay? Oh, my baby!

303
00:20:47,612 --> 00:20:49,739
告诉我 哪儿受伤了？
Talk to me, Where are you hurt?

304
00:20:49,814 --> 00:20:50,872
保罗？
Paul?

305
00:20:53,517 --> 00:20:54,677
噢 塔莎,
Oh, Tatsi,

306
00:20:57,054 --> 00:20:59,045
奥德特 奥德特！
Odette, Odette!

307
00:20:59,123 --> 00:21:00,112
噢 不
Oh, no,

308
00:21:00,191 --> 00:21:01,624
我没事
I'm okay,

309
00:21:01,692 --> 00:21:04,092
脱掉他的衣服 塔莎 弄点水来
Get his clothes off, Tatsi, please get some water,

310
00:21:04,161 --> 00:21:06,391
- 他受伤了 - 拜托 把他的衣服脱下来
- He's hurt, - Please, let's get his clothes off,

311
00:21:06,464 --> 00:21:08,864
- 他身上都是血 - 躺下 孩子
- He's covered in blood, - Lay back, son,

312
00:21:10,635 --> 00:21:12,626
他去隔壁齐朗戈家了
He went next door to the Chirangas,

313
00:21:13,537 --> 00:21:15,266
他哪儿受伤了？
Where is he hurt?

314
00:21:15,873 --> 00:21:17,932
看这儿 奥德特 看看这儿
Look here, Odette, look here,

315
00:21:18,009 --> 00:21:20,637
别动 罗杰 让他别动 保罗
Stay still, Roger, Keep him still, Paul,

316
00:21:21,479 --> 00:21:24,039
- 我找不到伤口 - 你怎么了？
- I can't find the wound, - What happened to you?

317
00:21:24,115 --> 00:21:25,514
- 告诉你妈妈 - 告诉我
- Tell your mother, - Talk to me,

318
00:21:25,583 --> 00:21:27,744
给你妈妈说怎么了 罗杰
Tell your mother what happened, Roger,

319
00:21:27,818 --> 00:21:29,251
罗杰 会没事的
Roger, you're okay,

320
00:21:29,320 --> 00:21:33,086
别担心 他没受伤 他没受伤
Do not worry, he is not cut, He is not hurt,

321
00:21:33,157 --> 00:21:35,591
这不是他的血 保罗
This is not his blood, Paul,

322
00:21:36,927 --> 00:21:38,258
你没有受伤
You are not hurt,

323
00:21:38,329 --> 00:21:41,787
亲爱的 没事儿 没事了
My darling, it's okay, It's okay,

324
00:21:41,866 --> 00:21:43,731
安全了 看着妈妈
