489
00:34:20,857 --> 00:34:23,155
我的房子被焚烧了 我无家可归
My house has been burned, I have nowhere to go,

490
00:34:23,226 --> 00:34:24,818
是的 我理解 阁下
Yes, I understand this, Your Honor,

491
00:34:24,895 --> 00:34:27,125
但我们正在腾房间
But we are operating at capacity as it is,

492
00:34:27,197 --> 00:34:31,031
我可以给你一个房间 但你们只能一起使用 抱歉
I can give you one room, but you will have to share it, I'm sorry,

493
00:34:31,101 --> 00:34:33,729
- 我们没法一起使用 - 抱歉 我很抱歉
- There's no way we can share, - I am sorry, Forgive me,

494
00:34:33,804 --> 00:34:35,271
我们有八个人呢
There are eight of us,

495
00:34:35,338 --> 00:34:36,896
- 怎么了？ - 保罗 来帮帮我
- Yes? - Paul, I need your help,

496
00:34:36,973 --> 00:34:38,133
好 阿彻夫人
Yes, Madame Archer,

497
00:34:45,582 --> 00:34:48,449
他们是圣弗朗西斯孤儿院的图西族儿童
They're Tutsi children from the St, Francis orphanage,

498
00:34:49,019 --> 00:34:50,680
好了 来 我们走
Okay, come on, let's go,

499
00:34:51,354 --> 00:34:54,221
- 我只剩一个房间了 - 没关系的
- I have only one room, - That'll do,

500
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:57,993
来
Come,

501
00:34:58,061 --> 00:35:00,461
- 奥托 拜托 - 抱歉
- Otto, please, - Excuse me,

502
00:35:01,531 --> 00:35:04,500
下士 请帮女士拎拎包 快点
Corporal, take that lady's bag, please, and quickly,

503
00:35:07,204 --> 00:35:10,605
- 我必须去接剩下的 - 剩下的？
- Have to go get the rest of them, - The rest of them?

504
00:35:10,674 --> 00:35:13,040
还有十个 我马上回来
There are another ten, I'll be back soon,

505
00:35:15,612 --> 00:35:17,546
阿彻夫人
Madame Archer,

506
00:35:17,614 --> 00:35:19,377
我想请您帮个忙
I have a favor to ask of you,

507
00:35:19,449 --> 00:35:22,976
我爱人的哥哥家 住在圣弗朗西斯附近
My brother-in-law and his family, they live near the St, Francis,

508
00:35:23,053 --> 00:35:25,146
奥克莱尔街 20号
On O'Clare, 20,

509
00:35:25,222 --> 00:35:28,214
您能帮忙带他们来吗？
Can you please get them and bring them here to me?

510
00:35:28,291 --> 00:35:30,316
- 没问题 - 我有照片
- Sure, - And I have a photo,

511
00:35:32,329 --> 00:35:34,024
拜托 继续搬！
Please, keep moving!

512
00:35:37,734 --> 00:35:39,395
- 谢谢 保罗 - 谢谢
- Thanks, Paul, - Thank you,

513
00:35:39,469 --> 00:35:41,334
谢谢搬进饭店！
Please move into the hotel!

514
00:35:41,404 --> 00:35:43,031
过来 孩子们 别害怕
Come on, kids, don't be afraid,

515
00:35:43,106 --> 00:35:45,802
- 带他们去后面 - 大伙儿 继续！
- Take them around the back, - Everyone, keep moving!

516
00:35:51,715 --> 00:35:54,115
他说话了吗？
Has he spoken to you yet?

517
00:35:54,184 --> 00:35:55,173
没有
No,

518
00:36:08,932 --> 00:36:10,957
你的脸上还是挂满了惆怅？
Is your face still hurting?

519
00:36:12,002 --> 00:36:13,162
没事儿
It's all right,

520
00:36:19,709 --> 00:36:22,439
邻居们叫我替他们对你的仁慈道谢
The neighbors asked me to thank you for your kindness,

521
00:36:25,182 --> 00:36:27,241
我不应该带他们来这儿
I shouldn't have brought them here,

522
00:36:29,252 --> 00:36:32,585
我得到职位时第一件被叮嘱的事就是
The first thing they told me when I received my appointment

523
00:36:32,656 --> 00:36:35,489
绝对、绝对不能降低饭店的品质
was to never, never lower the tone of the hotel,

524
00:36:36,893 --> 00:36:39,794
“一直要维持米尔・科林斯饭店的尊贵形象 保罗”
"Maintain the Mille Collines' dignity at all times, Paul,"

525
00:36:44,601 --> 00:36:46,592
这一切很快就会过去的
Soon all of this will be over,

526
00:36:49,105 --> 00:36:51,266
要是我失去了工作怎么办 塔莎？
What if I lose my job, Tatsi?

527
00:36:54,244 --> 00:36:55,302
噢 上帝！
Oh, my God!

528
00:36:55,378 --> 00:36:57,573
- 你去哪儿？ - 我马上回来
- Where are you going? - I'll be right back,

529
00:37:17,667 --> 00:37:19,601
照顾好他们
Take care of them,

530
00:37:19,669 --> 00:37:21,000
怎么做 先生？
How, sir?

531
00:37:22,339 --> 00:37:24,830
给他们洗澡 让他们吃东西
Bathe them, feed them,

532
00:37:26,243 --> 00:37:27,574
哄他们睡觉
Put them to bed,

533
00:37:30,680 --> 00:37:32,341
有事请我会帮你忙的
I will send you some help,

534
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,949
好了 宝贝们
Okay, babies,

535
00:37:39,289 --> 00:37:41,553
我们听说了报复性屠杀的行动
We have heard reports of reprisal massacres,

536
00:37:41,625 --> 00:37:44,116
联合国会出面制止流血事件的发生吗？
Will the U,N, intervene to stop the bloodshed?

537
00:37:44,194 --> 00:37:47,322
我们来这儿是为了维持和平 而非创造和平
We're here as peacekeepers, not as peacemakers,

538
00:37:47,397 --> 00:37:50,025
我下令不得对此加以干涉
My orders are not to intervene,

539
00:37:51,001 --> 00:37:52,901
- 抱歉 - 谢谢 上校
- Excuse me, - Thank you, Colonel,

540
00:37:53,603 --> 00:37:54,695
这儿 过来
Here, Over here,

541
00:37:54,771 --> 00:37:57,899
听着 我弄了辆车 我们必须马上离开
Listen, I got us a car, but we gotta move now,

542
00:37:58,642 --> 00:38:00,234
我们不能那样做 杰克
We're not allowed to do that, Jack,

543
00:38:00,310 --> 00:38:03,711
大卫 那些该死的东西会把墙推倒 我们必须有所防备
David, the shit's going down outside these walls, We gotta cover it,

544
00:38:03,780 --> 00:38:06,908
我们不会离开饭店的 除非有装甲车
We're not leaving the hotel grounds unless we have an armored car,

545
00:38:06,983 --> 00:38:09,144
- 这是章程 - 章程？
- That's the ground rules, - The ground rules?

546
00:38:09,219 --> 00:38:11,050
你以为我们这是在哪儿？他妈的温布尔登吗？
Where do you think we are, fucking Wimbledon?

547
00:38:11,121 --> 00:38:16,115
就此作罢 直到弄到合适的交通工具 杰克
We cover the story from here until we get the proper vehicles, Jack,

548
00:38:16,192 --> 00:38:18,626
去拍摄些名单B中的难民吧
Shoot some "B" roll of the refugees,

549
00:38:24,334 --> 00:38:25,562
我们走
Let's go,

550
00:38:25,635 --> 00:38:28,263
上校 我无法确保这些人的安全
Colonel, I have no way to protect these people,

551
00:38:28,338 --> 00:38:31,205
我这儿的房间装不下这么多难民
And I have more refugees than I have room for as it is,

552
00:38:31,274 --> 00:38:34,710
红十字会今天带来了20名孤儿
I was given 20 orphans today by the Red Cross,

553
00:38:34,778 --> 00:38:36,837
这儿不是难民营
This is not a refugee camp,

554
00:38:36,913 --> 00:38:39,108
你不能把他们带去你那儿吗？
Can you not take them with you to your facilities?

555
00:38:39,182 --> 00:38:42,447
不行 我不能那样 保罗 抱歉
No, I can't do that, Paul, I'm sorry,

556
00:38:43,353 --> 00:38:46,083
我的难民营很令人担忧
I'm overwhelmed at my refugee camp,

557
00:38:46,156 --> 00:38:48,750
那儿一直在打仗 持续的战斗
I'm under attack, constant attack,

558
00:38:48,825 --> 00:38:52,727
一旦我们控制住局势 我就带他们去那儿
As soon as we can stabilize this situation, then I'll take 'em,

559
00:38:55,665 --> 00:39:00,364
…防止那些试图逃脱审判的图西族蟑螂
...and stop the Tutsi cockroaches who try to run from justice.

560
00:39:00,437 --> 00:39:04,965
一名叫马吉萨的图西族法官躲在4个…
The Tutsi cockroach judge called Makesa is hiding at 4...

561
00:39:07,610 --> 00:39:11,944
- …喀布尔和他的同伙… - 关掉收音机
-... Kabulla and his cockroaches... - Turn that radio off,

562
00:39:12,749 --> 00:39:14,444
他的情况将被密切关注 他…
Watch out for him. He--

563
00:39:16,853 --> 00:39:20,619
回去工作 我们必须让饭店正常运作
And get back to work, We have a hotel to run,

564
00:39:20,690 --> 00:39:23,887
这儿没什么好干的了 老板都走了
There's no work here anyway, The boss has left,

565
00:39:23,960 --> 00:39:25,655
我就是你们的老板！
I am your boss!

566
00:39:39,075 --> 00:39:43,068
先生 卢旺达米尔・科林斯饭店来电 一号线
Sir, there's a call from the Mille Collines in Rwanda on line one.

567
00:39:43,146 --> 00:39:45,706
什么？你哪位？
Yes? Who am I speaking to?

568
00:39:46,416 --> 00:39:49,977
是的 先生 我是保罗・卢斯赛伯吉纳 客房经理
Yes, sir, Paul Rusesabagina, the house manager,

569
00:39:50,053 --> 00:39:52,146
上次你来这儿是我们见过面 提伦斯先生
I met you on your last visit here, Mr, Tillens,

570
00:39:52,222 --> 00:39:54,986
啊 是的 保罗 我记得
Ah, yes, Paul, I remember,

571
00:39:55,058 --> 00:39:56,821
情况怎么样了？
How are things there?

572
00:39:56,893 --> 00:39:59,191
很复杂 先生
The situation is difficult, sir.

573
00:40:00,563 --> 00:40:04,727
有部分董事觉得我们应该关闭米尔・科林斯饭店
Some of our directors believe we should close the Mille Collines

574
00:40:04,801 --> 00:40:06,826
直到动荡的局面结束
until this unrest is over,

575
00:40:06,903 --> 00:40:10,532
我对此拿不定主意 保罗 你觉得呢？
I'm not sure about that, Paul. What do you think?

576
00:40:13,042 --> 00:40:17,274
先生 那会对我们的声誉造成不良影响
Sir, that would be very bad for our reputation,

577
00:40:17,347 --> 00:40:21,613
米尔・科林斯饭店对于忠实的消费者来说就是一片平静的绿洲
The Mille Collines is an oasis of calm for all our loyal customers,

578
00:40:21,684 --> 00:40:24,915
比利时航空公司弃之不顾 他们会怎么想？
What would they think if Sabena deserted them now?

579
00:40:24,988 --> 00:40:28,082
我想你保证 联合国已经控制了一切 先生
I assure you, the United Nations have everything under control, sir,

580
00:40:29,592 --> 00:40:31,492
很好 保罗 很好
Very well, Paul, Very well,

581
00:40:31,561 --> 00:40:35,497
但如果形势变得更严峻 我们还得关闭
But if this thing gets worse, we must close,

582
00:40:35,565 --> 00:40:38,864
要是有什么需要我帮忙的 给我电话
If there is anything I can do, please call,

583
00:40:39,502 --> 00:40:42,994
先生 是的 我现在正有一件事需要你帮忙
Sir, yes, there is one thing I'm going to be needing from you right away,

584
00:40:44,340 --> 00:40:47,935
告诉大家 我这样请求大家显得很尴尬
Let me tell you, it was an embarrassment for me to have to ask for this,

585
00:40:48,745 --> 00:40:50,827
在场的大多数人都相互认识
Most of us in this room have known each other

586
00:40:50,827 --> 00:40:52,909
并在一起共事多年
and worked together for many years,

587
00:40:54,050 --> 00:40:58,043
真的需要我致函比利时方面
Is it really necessary for me to get a letter from Belgium

588
00:40:58,121 --> 00:40:59,850
来让你们继续工作吗？
for you to perform your duties?

589
00:41:04,427 --> 00:41:07,419
实际上 别在乎这封信
In fact, forget this letter,

590
00:41:07,497 --> 00:41:09,527
要是你们不想为我工作
If you don't want to work for me and 

591
00:41:09,527 --> 00:41:11,558
而情愿出去 那现在就离开吧
would rather be out there, then leave now,

592
00:41:16,806 --> 00:41:20,401
拜托 各位 回到工作岗位上去
Please, everyone, back to work,

593
00:41:26,182 --> 00:41:28,241
保罗 感谢你来
Paul, thank you for coming,

594
00:41:28,318 --> 00:41:30,081
空调不能用了
The air conditioner's on the blink,

595
00:41:30,081 --> 00:41:31,845
你能帮我看看吗？
is there any way you can have a look at it?

596
00:41:31,921 --> 00:41:33,786
- 这是我最后一天了 - 当然
- I'm just on a deadline, - Certainly,

597
00:41:33,857 --> 00:41:38,055
弗雷德 告诉我你何时收到卫星信号的 谢谢
Fred, let me know when you get the satellite feed, Thanks,

598
00:41:38,661 --> 00:41:42,620
弗莱明先生 我还给你带了些茶叶来 先生
Mr, Fleming, I brought you some tea as well, sir,

599
00:41:42,699 --> 00:41:44,132
谢谢 保罗
Thank you, Paul,

600
00:41:45,401 --> 00:41:47,699
你是沙漠里的一片绿洲
You're an oasis in the desert,

601
00:41:49,105 --> 00:41:51,266
…政府和军队的人
...the elements of the government and army

602
00:41:51,341 --> 00:41:55,072
正在效仿索马里的美国人的做法
are following the example of what happened to the Americans in Somalia.

603
00:41:55,144 --> 00:42:01,014
我认为他们意欲胁迫我们 试图袭击我们…
I think they intend to intimidate us, try to attack us, and...

604
00:42:01,084 --> 00:42:04,713
希望西方能考虑撤军
hope that the West will pull all its troops out.

605
00:42:04,787 --> 00:42:07,187
- 你认为他们会成功吗？ - 不 当然不会
- Do you think they'll succeed? - No, they won't.

606
00:42:07,257 --> 00:42:08,656
联合国维和部队就驻扎在这儿
The U. N. 's here to stay.

607
00:42:08,725 --> 00:42:10,386
总统的飞机被击落后
What about the outbreak of violence

608
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:12,428
暴力事件的情况如何？
since the shooting down of the president's plane?

609
00:42:12,495 --> 00:42:15,293
你到底在干什么？
What the hell do you think you're doing?

610
00:42:15,365 --> 00:42:18,425
我要对这些人的安全负责
I'm responsible for the safety of this crew,

611
00:42:21,004 --> 00:42:22,301
什么？
What is this?

612
00:42:52,402 --> 00:42:55,235
- 哪儿拍的？ - 沿途半英里处
- Where did you get this? - Half a mile down the road,

613
00:42:55,838 --> 00:42:57,635
弗雷德 我是大卫
Fred, it's David,

614
00:42:57,707 --> 00:43:00,540
我拿到了让人难以置信的录像 关于集体屠杀
I've got incredible footage, It's a massacre,

615
00:43:00,610 --> 00:43:03,306
死尸 以及弯刀
Dead bodies, machetes,

616
00:43:03,379 --> 00:43:06,507
如果我立即赶过去 你能播报晚间新闻吗？
If I get this through right away, can you make the evening news?

617
00:43:07,483 --> 00:43:08,575
好
Yeah,

618
00:43:13,856 --> 00:43:15,551
这个必须头条播报
You have to lead with this,

619
00:43:16,793 --> 00:43:18,852
我是说你 你来试试看
I point at you, you do a shot,

620
00:43:18,928 --> 00:43:22,921
你会得到两倍的偿还 看看是否所有的酒…
And you'll get a total double and see if all the drinking--

621
00:43:22,999 --> 00:43:25,024
- 抱歉 达格里什先生 - 嘿 保罗
- Excuse me, Mr, Daglish, - Hey, Paul,

622
00:43:25,802 --> 00:43:28,862
听我说 之前的事很抱歉
Listen, sorry about earlier,

623
00:43:28,938 --> 00:43:31,566
如果我知道你在那儿 我就不会…
If I'd known you were in there, I wouldn't have--

624
00:43:31,641 --> 00:43:36,442
你拍下这段录像我很高兴 全世界都能看到
I am glad that you have shot this footage and that the world will see it,

625
00:43:36,512 --> 00:43:39,606
这是我们有机会让人干涉的唯一办法
It is the only way we have a chance that people might intervene,

626
00:43:42,885 --> 00:43:47,219
不错 但要是没人来干涉 披露这些还会是好事吗？
Yeah, and if no one intervenes, is it still a good thing to show?

627
00:43:48,992 --> 00:43:52,928
人们看到这种暴行 怎么会不干涉呢？
How can they not intervene when they witness such atrocities?

628
00:43:52,996 --> 00:43:57,365
我认为如果人们看到这些录像…
I think if people see this footage,,,

629
00:43:58,468 --> 00:44:01,062
…他们会说 “噢 上帝 太恐怖了”
,,,they'll say, "Oh, my God, that's horrible,"

630
00:44:01,137 --> 00:44:02,968
然后便继续享用他们的晚餐
and then go on eating their dinners,

631
00:44:07,710 --> 00:44:10,873
我到底在想什么？听着 想去放松一下吗？
What the hell do I know? Listen, you wanna just relax?

632
00:44:10,947 --> 00:44:13,609
我还有事情要做 谢谢你的邀请
I have more work to do, I thank you for your offer,

633
00:44:13,683 --> 00:44:15,913
祝你晚上过得愉快 达格里什先生
Please enjoy your evening, Mr, Daglish,

634
00:44:19,956 --> 00:44:22,891
- 救命啊！请救救我们！求求你们了！ - 先生！先生！
- Help! Please help us! Please! - Sir! Sir!

635
00:44:22,959 --> 00:44:24,984
门口出事了
We've got trouble at the gate,

636
00:44:27,730 --> 00:44:30,358
请问这儿有医疗援助吗？
Can we have some medical assistance here, please?

637
00:44:30,433 --> 00:44:33,630
那群人 跟我来 离开那个地方
That group, come with me, Move out of the area,

638
00:44:33,703 --> 00:44:35,933
- 到这边来 起来 起来 - 好了 所有人都后退
- Here, get up, get up, - Right, fall back, everybody,

639
00:44:37,040 --> 00:44:39,031
本尼迪克特 怎么回事？
Benedict, what is happening?

640
00:44:39,108 --> 00:44:42,043
他们杀了所有人 妇女…
They're killing everyone, The lady,,,

641
00:44:42,111 --> 00:44:44,875
部族民兵包围了整个城市
The lnterhamwe have surrounded the whole town,

642
00:44:44,947 --> 00:44:46,107
快！
Come on!

643
00:44:46,649 --> 00:44:48,640
开路 马上
Cover the road, Now,

644
00:44:49,519 --> 00:44:51,077
站好岗
Stand your ground,

645
00:44:52,989 --> 00:44:54,047
坚持
Hold the line,

646
00:44:54,123 --> 00:44:56,489
别开枪！别开枪！
Do not shoot! Do not shoot!

