00:58:08,016 --> 00:58:09,779
起来 起来 起来
Get up, get up, get up,

821
00:58:11,753 --> 00:58:15,416
- 你是经理？ - 是的 先生 怎么？
- Are you the manager? - Yes, sir, What's the matter?

822
00:58:17,326 --> 00:58:19,123
所有人都马上离开饭店
Everyone must leave the hotel now,

823
00:58:19,194 --> 00:58:21,389
- 什么？ - 爸爸 怎么了？
- Why? - Papa, what's wrong?

824
00:58:21,463 --> 00:58:22,760
这是命令
It's an order,

825
00:58:24,266 --> 00:58:28,259
我需要点时间…20、30分钟…洗个澡
I need some time-- 20, 30 minutes--to take a shower,

826
00:58:29,671 --> 00:58:32,936
- 先生 人们都还在睡觉呢 - 这我管不着
- Sir, people are still sleeping, - I don't care,

827
00:58:34,877 --> 00:58:39,007
拜托 我给你们那点啤酒 你们先喝着
Please, let me get you some beers, You and your boys,

828
00:58:39,081 --> 00:58:42,141
我会马上下来 好吗？我会尽快
And I'll be down right away, all right? As quick as I can,

829
00:58:42,217 --> 00:58:45,209
- 给你十分钟时间 - 好的 先生 十分钟
- Ten minutes, - Yes, sir, ten minutes,

830
00:58:47,356 --> 00:58:49,483
- 散开 - 快 孩子们 快
- Get out of the way, - Quick, children, quickly,

831
00:58:49,558 --> 00:58:52,584
- 罗杰不在这儿 - 他去哪儿了？罗杰呢？
- Roger's not here, - Where is he? Where's Roger?

832
00:58:52,661 --> 00:58:53,821
床下
Under the bed,

833
00:58:55,330 --> 00:58:57,662
罗杰 是爸爸
Roger, It's Papa,

834
00:58:57,733 --> 00:58:59,633
他们走了 他们走了 他们走了
They've gone, They've gone, they've gone,

835
00:58:59,701 --> 00:59:01,999
来 来 快
Come, come, Come on,

836
00:59:05,908 --> 00:59:08,570
噢 亲爱的 好了 甜心 没事儿了
Oh, my darling, It's okay, sweetie, It's okay,

837
00:59:08,644 --> 00:59:10,908
来 没事儿 没事儿了
Come on, it's okay, It's okay,

838
00:59:10,979 --> 00:59:13,504
- 到房顶去 塔莎娜 - 房顶？
- Go to the roof, Tatiana, - The roof?

839
00:59:13,582 --> 00:59:15,777
是的 不错 马上去房顶
Yes, yes, go to the roof right now,

840
00:59:16,552 --> 00:59:19,146
是的 你好 请接比齐蒙戈将军
Yes, good day, General Bizimungu, please,

841
00:59:20,355 --> 00:59:22,118
他去哪儿了？
He is where?

842
00:59:22,190 --> 00:59:24,249
不 这让人无法接受
No, that is unacceptable,

843
00:59:24,326 --> 00:59:25,987
谁下令这样做的？
Who would order such a thing?

844
00:59:28,063 --> 00:59:30,395
是的 你们找到将军了吗？
Yes, did you find the general?

845
00:59:33,969 --> 00:59:36,301
先生们 来喝点酒
Gentlemen, please have some beer,

846
00:59:36,371 --> 00:59:37,963
把房客名单拿给我
Get me the guest list,

847
00:59:39,241 --> 00:59:40,401
是 先生
Yes, sir,

848
00:59:43,178 --> 00:59:44,167
喂？
Yes?

849
00:59:44,246 --> 00:59:47,000
抱歉 先生 我和基加利的保罗通了电话
Sorry, sir, but I have a call from Paul in Kigali.

850
00:59:47,000 --> 00:59:48,182
他说是紧急情况
He says it's urgent.

851
00:59:48,250 --> 00:59:50,184
保罗 你还好吗？
Paul, are you all right?

852
00:59:50,252 --> 00:59:51,776
我们遇到大麻烦了 先生
We have a big problem, sir.

853
00:59:51,853 --> 00:59:52,945
什么麻烦？
What?

854
00:59:53,021 --> 00:59:55,148
胡图族的军队来了
The Hutu army have come,

855
00:59:55,223 --> 00:59:57,783
他们命令我们…所有人…都离开饭店
They've ordered us-- all of us--out of the hotel,

856
00:59:57,859 --> 00:59:59,622
他们为什么这么做？
Why are they doing this?

857
00:59:59,695 --> 01:00:02,163
我向他们会将我们统统杀掉
I think they will kill us all,

858
01:00:02,230 --> 01:00:03,219
杀掉？
Kill?

859
01:00:04,866 --> 01:00:08,529
你的意思是…所有人？有多少人？
What do you mean,,,all? How many?

860
01:00:08,604 --> 01:00:13,473
工作人员100个 还有800多的房客
We have 100 staff and now more than 800 guests,

861
01:00:13,542 --> 01:00:15,533
- 800？！ - 是的 先生
- 800?! - Yes, sir.

862
01:00:15,611 --> 01:00:18,808
800人都是图西族和胡图族难民
There are now 800 Tutsi and Hutu refugees.

863
01:00:18,880 --> 01:00:21,440
我没有时间了 先生
I do not have much time left, sir,

864
01:00:25,220 --> 01:00:27,085
我要感谢你
I want to thank you

865
01:00:27,155 --> 01:00:29,453
为我以及我家人所做的一切
for everything that you have done for me and my family,

866
01:00:29,524 --> 01:00:32,652
并感谢我在比利时航空公司的所有朋友
and please thank all of my friends at Sabena.

867
01:00:34,162 --> 01:00:35,720
保罗 等等
Paul, wait,

868
01:00:36,298 --> 01:00:39,062
我要你先别挂电话 等在电话旁
I'm gonna put you on hold, Stay by the phone,

869
01:00:40,202 --> 01:00:43,000
- 你们的报纸呢？ - 我们没有报纸 先生
- Where are your papers? - We don't have any papers, sir,

870
01:00:43,071 --> 01:00:46,370
我们没有报纸 都在房里烧掉了
We don't have any papers, They got burnt in the house,

871
01:00:47,275 --> 01:00:49,937
路易斯 接通联合国 告诉他们发生的一切
Louis, get on to the U,N, Tell them what's happening,

872
01:00:50,012 --> 01:00:51,445
需要帮忙吗 先生？
Did you need something, sir?

873
01:00:51,513 --> 01:00:53,714
玛丽 给首相办公室打个电话
Mary, call the prime minister's office,

874
01:00:53,714 --> 01:00:55,916
就说我有话要立刻和他说
Tell them I must speak with him now,

875
01:00:55,984 --> 01:00:57,110
好的
Okay,

876
01:01:00,656 --> 01:01:02,214
保罗 在吗？
Paul, are you there?

877
01:01:03,058 --> 01:01:04,047
在 先生
Yes, sir,

878
01:01:04,126 --> 01:01:05,855
谁能制止这一切 我打电话去？
Who can I call to stop this?

879
01:01:08,397 --> 01:01:11,457
法国人 他们给胡图族提供武器的
The French, They supply the Hutu army,

880
01:01:12,768 --> 01:01:16,602
尽一切可能争取时间 我马上给你电话
Do everything you can to buy time, I'll call you right back,

881
01:01:21,054 --> 01:01:23,579
你在干什么 杜比？
What are you doing, Dube?

882
01:01:23,657 --> 01:01:26,592
那个中尉 先生 他要看房客的名单
The lieutenant, sir, he wants to see the guest list.

883
01:01:29,696 --> 01:01:32,859
- 再去给他们拿点啤酒来 - 渴吗 弟兄们？来点啤酒？
- Go and get these boys some more beer. - Thirsty, boy? You like beer?

884
01:01:32,933 --> 01:01:34,264
谢谢
Thank you.

885
01:01:37,171 --> 01:01:38,502
跟我来 拜托
Come with me, please.

886
01:01:43,143 --> 01:01:45,304
先生 这是两周前的
Sir, that was two weeks ago.

887
01:01:50,584 --> 01:01:52,074
给你 先生
Here you are, sir.

888
01:01:54,988 --> 01:01:57,354
安德森 亚瑟斯 布里亚…
Anderson, Arthurs, Boulier...

889
01:01:58,725 --> 01:02:00,215
这是什么？
What is this?

890
01:02:03,163 --> 01:02:04,653
房客名单 先生
It is the guest list, sir.

891
01:02:05,666 --> 01:02:07,759
你想骗我？
Are you trying to make a fool of me?

892
01:02:07,834 --> 01:02:12,931
没有 总统被杀后我们就停止登记姓名了
No. We stopped taking names after the president was murdered.

893
01:02:13,006 --> 01:02:14,752
这是仅有的房客名单 先生
This is the only guest list, sir.

894
01:02:14,752 --> 01:02:16,498
留下的没有一个是欧洲人！
There are no Europeans left!

895
01:02:17,611 --> 01:02:21,945
马上给我这儿所有蟑螂的名单
Get me the names of all the cockroaches in there now.

896
01:02:22,849 --> 01:02:25,784
- 这需要点时间 - 我们没时间了
- That will take time. - We don't have time.

897
01:02:25,852 --> 01:02:30,551
要是我拿不到名单 我就会找出叛徒
If I don't have the names so that I can pick out the traitors,

898
01:02:30,624 --> 01:02:33,457
然后杀了这儿的所有人
then I'll kill everyone in there.

899
01:02:34,962 --> 01:02:36,452
从你开始
Starting with you.

900
01:02:37,231 --> 01:02:38,755
快去
Leave.

901
01:02:41,168 --> 01:02:42,226
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

902
01:02:54,481 --> 01:02:55,880
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

903
01:02:56,550 --> 01:02:57,710
你给谁打了电话？
Who did you call?

904
01:02:58,885 --> 01:03:01,217
- 我给谁打了电话？ - 别对我撒谎！
- Who did I call? - Don't lie to me!

905
01:03:03,624 --> 01:03:05,615
你叫什么？
What is your name?

906
01:03:05,692 --> 01:03:08,024
卢斯赛伯吉纳
Rusesabagina.

907
01:03:09,129 --> 01:03:11,063
保罗・卢斯赛伯吉纳
Paul Rusesabagina.

908
01:03:11,565 --> 01:03:13,430
我记住你了
I'll remember you.

909
01:03:14,701 --> 01:03:16,100
我记住你了
I'll remember you.

910
01:03:17,070 --> 01:03:20,801
- 我们走 - 快点 我们走
- Let's go. - Come on, we're leaving.

911
01:03:30,350 --> 01:03:31,339
他们走了
They've gone.

912
01:03:34,688 --> 01:03:36,087
保罗 保罗
Paul. Paul.

913
01:03:38,759 --> 01:03:40,750
我真担心你
I was afraid for you.

914
01:03:42,095 --> 01:03:45,758
先生 比利时航空的主席来电找你
Sir, the president of Sabena is on the phone for you.

915
01:03:47,134 --> 01:03:49,068
我要去和他谈谈
I must talkwith this man.

916
01:03:54,908 --> 01:03:57,638
- 提伦斯先生 - 保罗 情况怎么样？
- Mr. Tillens. - Paul. what's going on?

917
01:03:57,711 --> 01:04:01,044
他们走了 谢谢 先生 你怎么做的？
They left. Thank you, sir. What did you do?

918
01:04:01,114 --> 01:04:04,208
我与法国总统办公室联系过了
I got through to the French president's office.

919
01:04:06,453 --> 01:04:08,785
呃 谢谢你 你挽救了我们
Well, thank you. You have saved our lives.

920
01:04:09,623 --> 01:04:14,253
我再三恳请法国和比利时派兵返回搭救你们
I pleaded with the French and the Belgians to go back and get you all.

921
01:04:15,195 --> 01:04:17,823
但恐怕他们不会这样做
I am afraid this is not going to happen.

922
01:04:19,499 --> 01:04:21,990
他们都是胆小怕事的人 保罗
They're cowards, Paul.

923
01:04:22,903 --> 01:04:26,634
卢旺达不会为他们赢得一张选票
Rwanda is not worth a single vote to any of them.

924
01:04:28,041 --> 01:04:30,976
无论是法国人、英国人、美国人
The French, the British, the Americans.

925
01:04:32,079 --> 01:04:33,740
很抱歉 保罗
I am sorry, Paul.

926
01:04:36,016 --> 01:04:37,108
谢谢
Thank you.

927
01:04:40,754 --> 01:04:42,381
不会有人来救援我们……
There will be no rescue...

928
01:04:43,824 --> 01:04:45,815
…来干涉我们的事儿了
...no intervention for us.

929
01:04:47,361 --> 01:04:49,693
我们只能靠自己
We can only save ourselves.

930
01:04:50,897 --> 01:04:53,058
你们很多人都认识些海外的有权势的人
Many of you know influential people abroad.

931
01:04:53,133 --> 01:04:54,623
你们要和这些人联系
You must call these people.

932
01:04:54,701 --> 01:04:57,727
拜托 把这些传真到这个号码 谢谢
Please, fax this to this number. Thank you.

933
01:04:57,804 --> 01:05:00,534
你们要告诉他们我们的遭遇
You must tell them what will happen to us.

934
01:05:02,209 --> 01:05:03,699
和他们说再见
Say good-bye.

935
01:05:06,646 --> 01:05:08,409
但当你们说再见时
But when you say good-bye,

936
01:05:08,482 --> 01:05:13,647
就好像通过电话你们能抓住他们的手一样
say it as though you are reaching through the phone and holding their hand.

937
01:05:14,554 --> 01:05:17,250
让他们知道 如果他们放手…
Let them know that if they let go of that hand...

938
01:05:19,359 --> 01:05:20,849
…你们就会死亡
...you will die.

939
01:05:24,197 --> 01:05:27,928
我们要让他们感到惭愧 以至于来帮助我们
We must shame them into sending help.

940
01:05:30,370 --> 01:05:35,330
最重要的是 这不是一个难民营
Most importantly, this cannot be a refugee camp.

941
01:05:35,409 --> 01:05:39,505
部族民兵认为米勒・科林斯饭店是一家四星级的比利时饭店
The lnterhamwe believe that the Mille Collines is a four-star Sabena hotel.

942
01:05:39,579 --> 01:05:43,276
这是唯一能让我们生存的方式
That is the only thing that is keeping us alive.

943
01:05:43,350 --> 01:05:45,284
账单打印好了吗？
Have you printed the bills?

944
01:05:46,787 --> 01:05:49,278
谢谢 拜托清除记录
Thank you. Now please erase the register.

945
01:05:49,356 --> 01:05:52,382
- 清除？ - 是的 我不希望看到有姓名出现
- Erase it? - Yes. I want no names to appear there.

946
01:05:53,093 --> 01:05:55,061
老板 木匠准备就绪
Boss, the carpenters are ready.

947
01:05:55,128 --> 01:05:57,858
让他们去掉所有房间门上的号码
Tell them to remove all of the numbers from the doors.

948
01:05:57,931 --> 01:05:59,956
- 加上什么？ - 什么都别加
- And put what? - And put nothing.

949
01:06:07,808 --> 01:06:10,470
你好 这是最后一个礼拜的账单
Good day. Here is your bill for the last week.

950
01:06:10,544 --> 01:06:13,206
如果你无法支付或不能支付
If you cannot pay or think you will not be able to pay,

951
01:06:13,280 --> 01:06:16,681
请到餐厅去 杜比会帮你处理 谢谢
please go to the banquet room and Dube will take care of you. Thank you.

952
01:06:20,821 --> 01:06:23,289
国务院认为是否…
Does the State Department have a view

953
01:06:23,356 --> 01:06:27,554
会发生种族屠杀呢？
as to whether or not what is happening could be genocide?

954
01:06:27,627 --> 01:06:31,028
我们有足够的证据表明种族屠杀行动已经发生
We have every reason to believe that acts of genocide have occurred.

955
01:06:31,097 --> 01:06:35,830
为了进行种族屠杀 采取了多少次行动？
How many acts of genocide does it take to make genocide?

956
01:06:35,902 --> 01:06:38,928
艾伦 这个问题我无法回答
Alan. that's just not a question that I'm in a position to answer.

957
01:06:39,005 --> 01:06:42,566
很明显 你没有孤立地使用…
Is it true that you have specific guidance

958
01:06:42,642 --> 01:06:45,133
“种族屠杀”这个说法 而总是使用…
not to use the word "genocide" in isolation.

959
01:06:45,212 --> 01:06:47,806
“**行动”的说法 是这样的吗？
but always to preface it with this word "acts of"?

960
01:06:49,349 --> 01:06:54,412
我尽可能使用我觉得最好的说法
I have guidance which I try to use as best as I can.

961
01:06:54,488 --> 01:06:56,046
我…
I have--

962
01:06:56,122 --> 01:06:58,556
我们在使用时要做到标准化
There are formulations that we are using

963
01:06:58,625 --> 01:07:01,617
以便我们保持一致性…
that we are trying to be consistent in our use of--

964
01:07:04,231 --> 01:07:06,028
抱歉这不是格兰奥兰治牌的酒
I'm sorry it is not Glenmorangie.

965
01:07:07,133 --> 01:07:08,794
只要是苏格兰威士忌就行
As long as it is scotch.

966
01:07:11,104 --> 01:07:14,835
你的白人朋友抛弃了你
Your white friends have abandoned you.

967
01:07:16,576 --> 01:07:19,238
- 看上去是如此 - 呃 别担心
- So it would seem. - Well, don't worry.

968
01:07:19,312 --> 01:07:22,611
- 我会照顾你的 - 你这么说我很高兴
- I will take care of you. - I'm glad to hear that

969
01:07:22,682 --> 01:07:25,617
因为我不知道 或许你愿意派几个警察
because I was wondering if perhaps you could spare us a few policemen.

970
01:07:25,685 --> 01:07:26,879
来保护我们 先生
To protect us, sir.

971
01:07:26,953 --> 01:07:29,945
- 警察都很忙 保罗 - 是的 我知道
- The police are very busy, Paul. - Yes, I'm aware of this.

972
01:07:30,023 --> 01:07:33,288
但我上次和比利时航空的主席提及时
But when I last spoke to the president of Sabena,

973
01:07:33,360 --> 01:07:36,761
他向我保证 无论谁帮助保护了比利时的财产
he assured me that anyone who helped protect Belgian property

974
01:07:36,830 --> 01:07:38,320
都会得到很好的回报的
would be well rewarded.

975
01:07:39,332 --> 01:07:40,663
我看看我能不能帮忙
I will see what I can do.

976
01:07:41,835 --> 01:07:43,496
抱歉离开一下 先生
Excuse me momentarily, sir.

977
01:07:45,238 --> 01:07:47,001
我们所有的啤酒哪儿去了？
Where has all our beer gone?

978
01:07:48,008 --> 01:07:50,738
先生 格莱戈瓦拿走了啤酒
Sir, Gregoire has been taking beer.

979
01:07:51,444 --> 01:07:52,843
多少？
How much beer?

980
01:07:53,780 --> 01:07:54,872
很多
Many.

981
01:07:58,251 --> 01:08:01,186
…下来参加招待会 然后他对我说
...come down to the reception. And then he says to me,

982
01:08:01,254 --> 01:08:02,881
“想要姑娘吗？”
"How do you want the girls?"

983
01:08:04,858 --> 01:08:07,793
那是我们的蟑螂经理 喜欢亲别人屁股
There's our cockroach manager. Always kissing ass.

984
01:08:13,500 --> 01:08:14,660
将军…
General...

985
01:08:16,403 --> 01:08:18,132
很高兴你能来
I'm glad you came by.

986
01:08:18,905 --> 01:08:21,373
我无意中听到一些传言 我想你应该知道
I overheard something that I think you should know about.

987
01:08:21,441 --> 01:08:22,669
你听到什么？
What did you overhear?

988
01:08:22,742 --> 01:08:27,008
联合国上校和美国使馆官员的讨论
It was a discussion between a U.N. Colonel and an American Embassy official.

989
01:08:27,080 --> 01:08:28,479
他们说什么？
And what did they say?

990
01:08:28,548 --> 01:08:31,381
美国人向上校保证 他们会关注一切的
The American assured the colonel that they would watch everything.

991
01:08:31,451 --> 01:08:33,009
怎么关注？他们都打道回府了 保罗
How? They have gone, Paul.

992
01:08:33,086 --> 01:08:36,180
利用间谍、卫星
With their spies. Satellites.

993
01:08:38,692 --> 01:08:40,523
美国人啊
Americans.

994
01:08:40,594 --> 01:08:42,494
噢 格莱戈瓦！
Oh, Gregoire!

995
01:08:46,299 --> 01:08:48,199
知道吗 我很钦佩你 将军
You know, I admire you, General.

996
01:08:48,902 --> 01:08:51,700
你是如何管住这些疯狂的士兵的？
How do you keep command of your men amid such madness?

997
01:08:51,771 --> 01:08:55,537
- 我是个强人 保罗 - 希望我也能像你一样
- I am a strong man, Paul. - I wish I were more like you.

998
01:08:56,476 --> 01:08:58,842
- 我是说 看看我的雇员 - 干杯
- I mean, look at my staff. - Cheers.

999
01:08:58,912 --> 01:09:01,574
他们都不工作了 谁也不听
He won't work, listens to no one.

1000
01:09:01,648 --> 01:09:04,242
- 他是雇员吗？ - 噢 是的
- He is staff? - Oh, yes.

1001
01:09:04,317 --> 01:09:05,306
是的
Yes.

1002
01:09:16,062 --> 01:09:18,223
回去工作 你这个懒人！快去！
Get back to work, you slug! Go!

1003
01:09:19,599 --> 01:09:21,032
卫星？
Satellites?

1004
01:09:22,202 --> 01:09:25,694
我还想说 美国人就藏在树林里呢
What was I going to say, that the Americans were hiding in the trees?

1005
01:09:37,751 --> 01:09:41,551
- 有什么不妥？ - 我得出去找点吃的回来
- What's the matter? - I have to go out and get food.

1006
01:09:41,621 --> 01:09:45,557
- 出去？去哪儿？ - 去乔治・卢塔甘达那儿
- Go out? Where? - To George Rutaganda's place.

1007
01:09:45,625 --> 01:09:47,752
不 不 不
No. No, no.

1008
01:09:47,827 --> 01:09:49,658
我必须去 塔莎娜
I have to, Tatiana.

1009
01:09:49,729 --> 01:09:52,357
只有给他钱的时候 我们才有点价值
We are only as valuable as the money we give to him.

1010
01:09:52,432 --> 01:09:54,093
你不能单独去
You cannot go alone.

1011
01:09:54,968 --> 01:09:58,631
我不会一个人去 我会带上格莱戈瓦
I'm not going alone. I'll take Gregoire with me.

1012
01:09:58,705 --> 01:10:01,936
他是胡图族人 现在他又想在我面前挣表现
He's a good Hutu, and he wants to impress me now.

1013
01:10:11,785 --> 01:10:13,946
很高兴你还在工作 格莱戈瓦
It is good to see you back at work, Gregoire.

1014
01:10:14,020 --> 01:10:17,080
- 拜托 先生 请接受我得道歉 - 拜托 拜托
- Please, sir, accept my humblest apologies. - Please, please.

1015
01:10:17,957 --> 01:10:19,788
早上我们有个工作
We have a job this morning.

1016
01:10:19,859 --> 01:10:22,191
我们要去看看乔治・卢塔甘达
We are going to see George Rutaganda.

1017
01:10:23,263 --> 01:10:24,594
去把车开过来
Please get the van.

1018
01:10:44,350 --> 01:10:45,840
给我看看你的身份证
Show me your l.D.

1019
01:10:45,919 --> 01:10:48,410
还记得图西族妇女习惯于…
Remember how those Tutsi women used to look down

1020
01:10:48,488 --> 01:10:50,001
低下她们的长鼻梁看胡图族人吗？
their long noses at Hutu men?

1021
01:10:50,001 --> 01:10:51,514
现在她们要为他们的生命而祈祷
Now they beg for their lives.

1022
01:10:51,591 --> 01:10:54,116
我来这儿看我的朋友乔治・卢塔甘达
I'm here to see my friend George Rutaganda.

1023
01:10:54,194 --> 01:10:58,563
在图西族下流女人死之前 建议大家先去尝尝她们的味道
I say taste those Tutsi whores before they die.

1024
01:10:58,631 --> 01:11:02,158
这样她们才知道到底什么是胡图族政权 我的勇士们
Then they'll know what Hutu power is. my warriors.

1025
01:11:02,235 --> 01:11:06,001
记住 每一只蟑螂都会发动奇袭
Remember. one cockroach can start an infestation.

1026
01:11:06,072 --> 01:11:08,540
我们要彻底铲除这些害虫
We need to exterminate these vermin.

1027
01:11:39,272 --> 01:11:41,638
嘿 保罗 我的老朋友
Hey, Paul, my old friend.

1028
01:11:45,078 --> 01:11:49,037
是图西族妓女 找我有什么事儿？
Tutsi prostitutes and witches. So, what can I do for you?

1029
01:11:49,783 --> 01:11:52,377
- 我需要点补给品 乔治 - 随时都可以
- I need supplies, George. - Anytime.

1030
01:11:57,457 --> 01:12:01,052
保罗 所有的东西价格都翻倍了 知道吗？
Paul, everything is double the price now. You understand that?

1031
01:12:01,127 --> 01:12:04,290
知道 我需要大米、豆荚
Yes. I need rice, beans,

1032
01:12:04,364 --> 01:12:07,765
奶粉、啤酒 还有你最好的威士忌
powdered milk, beer, and your best whiskey.

1033
01:12:08,935 --> 01:12:12,427
啤酒有 但威士忌没有
Beer yes, but whiskey no.

1034
01:12:12,505 --> 01:12:14,063
没有威士忌？
You have no whiskey?

1035
01:12:14,140 --> 01:12:16,836
没有威士忌 烈酒都没有了
No whiskey, no spirits.

1036
01:12:16,910 --> 01:12:21,643
你那些…富有的房客们只能忍受一下了
Your...rich guests will have to do without their scotch.

1037
01:12:22,248 --> 01:12:25,740
总之 保罗 我已经让那些牛流够了血
Anyway, Paul, I have bled that cow enough now.

1038
01:12:26,853 --> 01:12:28,377
你在说什么 乔治？
What are you saying, George?

1039
01:12:28,454 --> 01:12:31,252
你饭店里的那些富有的蟑螂
Your rich cockroaches at the hotel,

1040
01:12:31,252 --> 01:12:34,051
他们拿着钱没有用的
their money is no good to them anymore.

1041
01:12:34,894 --> 01:12:37,124
很快所有的图西族人都得死
Soon all the Tutsis will be dead.

1042
01:12:39,699 --> 01:12:42,964
你难道没有想过 你不可能将他们杀绝的？
You do not honestly believe that you can kill them all?

1043
01:12:44,337 --> 01:12:45,736
为什么不能？
And why not?

1044
01:12:47,373 --> 01:12:48,965
为什么不能？
Why not?

1045
01:12:49,042 --> 01:12:51,533
我们已经杀掉一半了
We are halfway there already.

1046
01:12:54,347 --> 01:12:57,214
保罗 你要12袋大米？
So, Paul, you want 12 bags of rice?

1047
01:12:58,418 --> 01:13:01,012
给他12袋大米和4箱啤酒
Give him 12 bags of rice and 4 crates of beer.

1048
01:13:01,087 --> 01:13:02,577
好的 先生 马上
Yes, sir, right away.

1049
01:13:04,123 --> 01:13:09,925
噢 还有 保罗 我免费给你一箱饮料 拿给孩子们喝
Oh, and, Paul, I'll give you a crate of soft drinks for the kids free of charge.

1050
01:13:11,431 --> 01:13:12,523
好的
Yes.

1051
01:13:14,267 --> 01:13:16,997
十袋豆荚 来 快点
Ten bags of beans. Come, quick.

1052
01:13:17,637 --> 01:13:20,162
都装上车 你
And put those in the van. You.

1053
01:13:21,774 --> 01:13:23,765
我要提醒一下你 朋友
Let me give you a little tip, my friend.

1054
01:13:23,843 --> 01:13:26,573
我们军队将军说 “别靠近米勒・科林斯饭店
Our generals in army say, "Don't go near the Mille Collines

1055
01:13:26,646 --> 01:13:28,841
否则他们会派比利时士兵来这儿”
or they will send the Belgian soldiers back here."

1056
01:13:28,915 --> 01:13:33,181
很快这些将军会离开 由我们负责
But soon those generals will have gone and we will be in charge.

1057
01:13:34,420 --> 01:13:38,652
到时候就开始屠宰你的肥牛了
It's time to butcher that fat cow of yours for the meat.

1058
01:13:49,569 --> 01:13:50,968
我们走
Let's go.

1059
01:13:53,907 --> 01:13:55,898
或许你可以帮我 保罗
Maybe you could help us, Paul.

1060
01:13:55,975 --> 01:13:58,842
你旅馆里有很重要的叛徒
You have some very important traitors at that hotel.

1061
01:13:59,512 --> 01:14:01,343
如果我们去把他们抓来
Now, if we were to get them,

1062
01:14:01,414 --> 01:14:05,214
或许我们会让你留下一两只蟑螂在你身边
then maybe we would let you have one or two cockroaches of your own.

1063
01:14:07,153 --> 01:14:08,552
明白吗？
Do you understand?

1064
01:14:10,590 --> 01:14:13,423
天快亮了 乔治
It is almost dawn, George.

1065
01:14:13,493 --> 01:14:15,586
我们真的要走了
We really must be going.

1066
01:14:17,363 --> 01:14:20,560
回去时走河边 比较安全
Take the river road back. It's clear.

1067
01:14:42,255 --> 01:14:44,849
- 格莱戈瓦 - 怎么了？
- Gregoire. - What is going on now?

1068
01:14:44,924 --> 01:14:47,154
- 你开出路了 - 不 我在路上
- You've driven off the road. - No, I'm on the road.

1069
01:14:47,226 --> 01:14:50,059
你要让我们都掉河里去？停车 停车
You're going to put us in the river. Stop the car, stop the car.

1070
01:16:14,614 --> 01:16:16,309
倒车 格莱戈瓦
Back up the car, Gregoire.

1071
01:16:18,217 --> 01:16:19,377
听我说
Listen to me.

1072
01:16:20,987 --> 01:16:24,150
今天看到的对谁都别讲
You will tell no one what you have seen here today.

1073
01:16:24,223 --> 01:16:25,622
谁都别讲 格莱戈瓦
No one, Gregoire.

1074
01:16:41,941 --> 01:16:45,934
杜比 去帮格莱戈瓦卸货 谢谢
Dube. Please help Gregoire to unload the van. Thank you.

1075
01:17:20,279 --> 01:17:21,678
噢 亲爱的
Oh, dear.

1076
01:17:53,813 --> 01:17:55,075
噢 上帝！
Oh, God!

1077
01:17:58,284 --> 01:17:59,512
噢 上帝！
Oh, God!

1078
01:18:00,720 --> 01:18:02,051
- 先生 - 杜比！
- Sir. - Dube!

1079
01:18:02,121 --> 01:18:05,989
- 先生 你没事儿吧？ - 别进来 别进来
- Sir, are you okay? - Don't come in. Don't come in.

1080
01:18:06,058 --> 01:18:08,049
我马上出来
I'll be out in a minute.

1081
01:18:09,328 --> 01:18:12,161
- 先生 你没事儿吧？ - 是的 我没事儿 杜比
- Sir, are you okay? - Yes, I'm all right, Dube.

1082
01:18:13,065 --> 01:18:14,862
别进来 我就出来
Don't come in. I'll be out.

1083
01:18:49,168 --> 01:18:50,430
成百上千
Hundreds.

1084
01:18:53,172 --> 01:18:55,265
不计其数
It was too many to count.

1085
01:18:58,811 --> 01:19:01,279
为什么这些人这么残忍？
Why are people so cruel?

1086
01:19:05,251 --> 01:19:06,411
憎恨
Hatred.

1087
01:19:07,887 --> 01:19:09,718
疯了 不知道
Insanity. I don't know.

1088
01:19:15,428 --> 01:19:16,452
拿去
There you go.

1089
01:19:16,529 --> 01:19:18,827
她把手指伸进汤里了？
Is she putting her fingers in the soup?

1090
01:19:18,898 --> 01:19:20,798
噢 是的
Oh, yes.

1091
01:19:21,968 --> 01:19:24,459
…和你 和你无关
...to do with you. Nothing to do with me.

1092
01:19:24,537 --> 01:19:25,936
我记得…
I remember...

1093
01:19:27,039 --> 01:19:28,768
不 不 不 你错了
No, no, no, you make a mistake.

1094
01:19:28,841 --> 01:19:30,536
- 嗨 - 跟我来
- Hello. - Come with me.

1095
01:19:32,545 --> 01:19:34,479
- 我们去哪儿？ - 来
- Where are we going? - Just come.

1096
01:19:51,330 --> 01:19:52,661
很美
It's beautiful.

1097
01:19:54,667 --> 01:19:55,929
喜欢吗？
You like it?

1098
01:20:05,411 --> 01:20:07,811
听说我们得偿还这一切
I hear we must pay for everything.

1099
01:20:07,880 --> 01:20:09,370
是的 不错
Yes, this is true.

1100
01:20:10,683 --> 01:20:14,175
那…这个值多少？
So...how much for this?

1101
01:20:16,188 --> 01:20:17,678
一个吻
A kiss.

1102
01:20:29,535 --> 01:20:34,370
你是个好人 保罗・卢斯赛伯吉纳
You are a good man, Paul Rusesabagina.

1103
01:20:51,057 --> 01:20:52,649
我像你坦白一件事
I have a confession.

1104
01:20:54,727 --> 01:20:56,718
当你还是个护士的时候…
When you worked as the nurse...

1105
01:20:56,796 --> 01:20:58,957
- 在鲁亨盖里？ - 是的
- In Ruhengeri? - Yes.

1106
01:20:59,031 --> 01:21:01,056
我们第一次见面…
When we first met...

1107
01:21:02,635 --> 01:21:05,126
是我让你调到了基加里
I had you transferred to Kigali.

1108
01:21:07,473 --> 01:21:08,804
什么？
What?

1109
01:21:09,775 --> 01:21:14,269
我贿赂了卫生部长 把你调到了基加里
I bribed the Minister of Health to have you transferred to Kigali.

1110
01:21:16,148 --> 01:21:18,742
- 为什么？ - 这样我们更近些
- Why? - To be closer.

1111
01:21:20,219 --> 01:21:21,948
这样我才能娶你
So that I could marry you.

1112
01:21:28,627 --> 01:21:29,958
你贿赂了什么？
What was the bribe?

1113
01:21:32,765 --> 01:21:35,928
- 我对你来说值多少？ - 很多
- What am I worth to you? - It was substantial.

1114
01:21:36,001 --> 01:21:38,834
- 告诉我是什么 - 一辆车
- Tell me what it was. - A car.

1115
01:21:40,940 --> 01:21:43,773
- 什么车？ - 这有关系吗？
- What sort of car? - What does that matter?

1116
01:21:43,843 --> 01:21:45,708
我想知道
I want to know.

1117
01:21:47,279 --> 01:21:48,871
大众
A Volkswagen.

1118
01:21:53,886 --> 01:21:55,217
希望是一辆新的
I hope it was a new one.

1119
01:22:20,312 --> 01:22:23,475
我的一生是幸福的 你和我 是的
We have had a good life, you and l. Yes.

1120
01:22:26,452 --> 01:22:31,048
感谢上帝 我们共同度过的每一天
I thank God every day for the time we've had.

1121
01:22:37,096 --> 01:22:40,998
- 我们必须得有个计划 - 计划？
- We have to have a plan. - A plan?

1122
01:22:42,868 --> 01:22:45,860
孩子们不能看着我们先死去
Our children cannot see us die first.

1123
01:22:45,938 --> 01:22:49,339
要使民兵来了 你尽快到这上面来
If the militia come, you must come up here as quick as you can.

1124
01:22:49,408 --> 01:22:52,070
- 拜托 我不想… - 你必须上来 塔莎娜
- Please, I don't want to-- - You must come up here, Tatiana.

1125
01:22:52,144 --> 01:22:55,079
- 我不想听你这样说 拜托 - 我们必须得说 塔莎娜
- I don't want you to talk like this, please. - We have to, Tatiana.

1126
01:22:56,882 --> 01:22:59,282
如果我没有挺过来
If I do not make it,

1127
01:22:59,351 --> 01:23:02,149
你一定要牵着孩子们的手…
you must take all of our children by the hand...

1128
01:23:03,923 --> 01:23:05,254
…你一定要跳
...and you must jump.

1129
01:23:07,326 --> 01:23:10,659
- 你在说什么？我不会… - 你必须如此 塔莎娜
- What are you saying? I could never-- - You have to, Tatiana.

1130
01:23:10,729 --> 01:23:13,493
- 你向我保证 - 你在说什么？
- You have to promise me. - What are you saying?

1131
01:23:13,566 --> 01:23:15,215
塔莎娜 不要死在弯刀下
Tatiana, the machete is no way to die.

1132
01:23:15,215 --> 01:23:16,865
你得向我保证你会那样做
You have to promise me you will do it.

1133
01:23:16,936 --> 01:23:18,665
我不…
I cannot do--

1134
01:23:18,737 --> 01:23:21,501
你必须向我保证 塔莎娜 拜托
You have to promise me, Tatiana. Please.

1135
01:23:21,574 --> 01:23:23,166
向我保证你会那样做
Promise me you will do it.

1136
01:23:26,812 --> 01:23:28,643
拜托 塔莎娜
Please, Tatiana.

1137
01:23:31,784 --> 01:23:32,944
好
Yes.

1138
01:23:35,788 --> 01:23:37,517
抱歉 我爱你
I'm sorry. I love you.

1139
01:23:39,258 --> 01:23:40,589
我爱你
I love you.

1140
01:23:48,467 --> 01:23:49,957
我要抓住你！
I'm gonna get you!

1141
01:23:51,403 --> 01:23:53,394
黛安 伊利 你最好知道
Diane, Elys, you know better.

1142
01:23:53,472 --> 01:23:55,997
谁都不能到饭店前面来 我给你说过
No one can be at the front of the hotel. I have told you this.

1143
01:23:56,075 --> 01:23:58,373
- 带孩子们去后面 快 - 抱歉 爸爸
- Take these children in the back. Hurry. - Sorry, Papa.

1144
01:23:59,578 --> 01:24:01,409
- 来 孩子们 来 - 谢谢 杜比
- Come, children. Come. - Thank you, Dube.

1145
01:24:04,149 --> 01:24:07,380
保罗 我有好消息了
Paul, I've got good news.

1146
01:24:10,389 --> 01:24:14,120
祝贺你们 你们的电话起作用了
Congratulations. Your calls have worked.

1147
01:24:14,193 --> 01:24:17,993
我拿到了这些家庭的出境签证
I have exit visas for the following families.

1148
01:24:18,063 --> 01:24:21,260
阿布克苏 坦桑尼亚
Abukesu, Tanzania.

1149
01:24:21,333 --> 01:24:24,325
比多利 肯尼亚
Bidori, Kenya.

1150
01:24:26,238 --> 01:24:28,331
基图朗伽 赞比亚
Gituaranga, Zambia.

1151
01:24:28,407 --> 01:24:30,170
哈利路亚！（赞美上帝）
Hallelujah!

1152
01:24:30,242 --> 01:24:31,903
喀里萨 比利时
Khalesa, Belgium.

1153
01:24:31,977 --> 01:24:33,137
噢 谢谢！
Oh, thank you!

1154
01:24:34,313 --> 01:24:35,712
达库兹…
Dakuzi...

1155
01:24:37,283 --> 01:24:38,545
肯尼亚
Kenya.

1156
01:24:39,418 --> 01:24:42,182
纳桑波 赞比亚
Masambo, Zambia.

1157
01:24:43,422 --> 01:24:45,754
辛咕噜 加纳
Zinguru, Ghana.

1158
01:24:45,824 --> 01:24:48,884
卢斯赛伯吉纳 比利时
Rusesabagina, Belgium.

1159
01:24:50,162 --> 01:24:51,629
好了 就这些
All right, that's it.

1160
01:24:53,098 --> 01:24:56,090
记住 这些家庭早上7点前做好准备
So remember, families be ready at 7 a.m.

1161
01:24:56,168 --> 01:24:57,430
我们走
Let's go.

1162
01:24:57,503 --> 01:24:58,561
- 上校？ - 什么
- Colonel? - Yeah.

1163
01:24:59,638 --> 01:25:01,833
奥德特和吉恩・巴提斯一定在名单上
Now, certainly Odette and Jean Baptiste are on the list.

1164
01:25:01,907 --> 01:25:04,740
抱歉 吉恩 奥德特
I'm sorry, Jean, Odette.

1165
01:25:05,911 --> 01:25:09,472
但我保证不久又会有另一班飞机的
But I have been assured there will be another plane soon.

1166
01:25:09,548 --> 01:25:10,537
抱歉
Excuse me.

1167
01:25:13,052 --> 01:25:16,112
别担心 塔莎 下一批会有的
Don't worry, Tatsi, we'll make it to the next list.

1168
01:25:16,188 --> 01:25:17,177
是的
Yeah.

1169
01:25:18,791 --> 01:25:21,726
女孩…保罗 我不会留下她们而去
The girls-- Paul, I will not leave without them.

1170
01:25:31,737 --> 01:25:33,068
你带了些什么来？
What have you brought us?

1171
01:25:33,138 --> 01:25:36,471
抗生素、药物补给、一般急救用品
Antibiotics, medical supplies, general first aid.

1172
01:25:36,542 --> 01:25:38,032
谢谢
Thank you.

1173
01:25:38,110 --> 01:25:40,601
- 听说有航班来接了 - 是的
- I hear there's to be a convoy. - Yes.

1174
01:25:40,679 --> 01:25:42,408
名单上有你吗？
Are you on the list?

1175
01:25:45,884 --> 01:25:50,617
阿彻夫人 我有个难以接受的请求
Madame Archer, I have an impossible request of you.

1176
01:25:51,590 --> 01:25:54,855
你有办法去那位老太太那儿
Is there any way that you could return to the old woman

1177
01:25:54,927 --> 01:25:56,918
把我的侄女带过来吗？
and bring the girls back here to us?

1178
01:25:56,996 --> 01:26:00,955
保罗 半个城市在战斗中都被摧毁了
Paul, that side of town has been destroyed in the fighting.

1179
01:26:01,900 --> 01:26:03,231
他们很可能已经死了
They're probably dead.

1180
01:26:06,305 --> 01:26:09,638
阿彻夫人 我求求你了 她们现在无亲无故
Madame Archer, I'm begging you. Those girls have no one now.

1181
01:26:13,412 --> 01:26:14,902
我尽力而为
I'll try.

1182
01:26:16,048 --> 01:26:18,141
我早上7就要离开了
We have to leave by 7 a.m.

1183
01:26:18,651 --> 01:26:20,744
你走了谁来照顾孤儿们？
Who'll take care of the orphans when you're gone?

1184
01:26:20,819 --> 01:26:24,482
奥德特 奥德特会照料他们 直到我们带他们离开这儿
Odette. Odette will care for them until we can get them out of here.

1185
01:26:28,694 --> 01:26:32,687
保罗 你说说 哪个国家会接受这20名卢旺达孤儿？
Tell me, Paul, what country's gonna take 20 Rwandan orphans?

1186
01:26:32,765 --> 01:26:36,496
我会找到人的 我向你保证
I will find someone. I promise you.

1187
01:26:38,737 --> 01:26:40,864
- 谢谢 - 谢谢
- Thanks. - Thank you.

1188
01:26:48,380 --> 01:26:49,779
来 牵着我手
Come on, take my hand.

1189
01:26:50,382 --> 01:26:53,715
非洲新闻播报 今天红十字代表声称
News Service Africa. Today a Red Cross representative

1190
01:26:53,786 --> 01:26:56,346
卢旺达种族冲突的死亡路进一步攀升
claimed that the death rate in the Rwandan conflict

1191
01:26:56,422 --> 01:26:59,983
死亡人数达500,000
may have climbed to as many as 500.000 victims.

1192
01:27:00,059 --> 01:27:02,459
一个报道称有40,000具
One report stated that 40.000 bodies

1193
01:27:02,528 --> 01:27:04,758
尸体被遗弃在维多利亚湖
had been removed from Lake Victoria.

1194
01:27:06,632 --> 01:27:07,656
她在哪儿？
Where is she?

1195
01:27:07,733 --> 01:27:11,499
不知道 我们等到七点
I don't know. We wait until seven.

1196
01:27:11,570 --> 01:27:13,970
如果到时候他没有带回姑娘们…
If she is not back with the girls by then...

1197
01:27:15,340 --> 01:27:16,830
…她就可能不会来了
...she may not be coming.

1198
01:27:19,645 --> 01:27:20,634
谢谢
Thank you.

1199
01:27:20,713 --> 01:27:22,943
拜托 带着这些邮件
Please, take these letters.

1200
01:27:23,015 --> 01:27:25,279
好的 我会带着的
Yes, I will take your letters.

1201
01:27:25,350 --> 01:27:27,818
太感谢你了 保罗 带着这些邮件
Thank you so much, Paul, taking the letter.

1202
01:27:29,354 --> 01:27:32,187
- 非常感谢 - 是的 抱歉
- Thank you so much. - Yes, I am sorry.

1203
01:27:32,257 --> 01:27:33,417
非常感谢
Thank you very much.

1204
01:27:33,492 --> 01:27:36,256
抱歉 希望我能帮你们更多 抱歉
I am sorry. I wish I could have done more. I am sorry.

1205
01:27:38,564 --> 01:27:40,395
上帝与你同在
God be with you.

1206
01:27:41,800 --> 01:27:44,963
- 是的 你有孩子吗？ - 是的 你可以走了
- Yes, do you have any children? - Yes, you're clear to go.

1207
01:27:46,305 --> 01:27:48,136
不 抱歉 没用的
No, sorry, no good.

1208
01:27:48,640 --> 01:27:51,006
来 来 孩子们
Come. Come, children.

1209
01:27:51,076 --> 01:27:52,805
塔莎 来
Tatsi, come.

1210
01:27:54,680 --> 01:27:57,012
拜托 保罗 姑娘们 我们在等一下吧
Please, Paul, the girls. We wait a little longer.

1211
01:27:57,082 --> 01:27:59,073
我们不能等了 不能等了 塔莎
We cannot wait. We cannot wait, Tatsi.

1212
01:27:59,151 --> 01:28:00,140
来吧
There you go.

1213
01:28:00,786 --> 01:28:02,117
出发！
Let's move out!

1214
01:28:05,824 --> 01:28:07,155
好运 先生
Good luck, sir.

1215
01:28:18,570 --> 01:28:23,166
我不能走 你拉着塔莎娜 照顾我的家人
I am not leaving. You hold Tatiana. Take care of my family.

1216
01:28:29,348 --> 01:28:30,838
保罗 保罗！
Paul. Paul!

1217
01:28:32,017 --> 01:28:35,509
我不能眼睁睁看着这些人去死 我不能留下这些人不管
I cannot leave these people to die. I cannot leave these people.

1218
01:28:35,587 --> 01:28:36,849
爸爸！
Papa!

1219
01:28:36,922 --> 01:28:39,891
罗杰！罗杰 我会乘下一班飞机的
Roger! Roger, I will follow on the next flight.

1220
01:28:39,958 --> 01:28:42,722
不 别扔下我！保罗！
No, don't leave me! Paul!

1221
01:28:42,795 --> 01:28:46,253
别担心 别担心 孩子们 你爸爸没事儿的
Don't worry. Don't worry, children. Your father's going to be okay.

1222
01:28:46,331 --> 01:28:47,355
爸爸！
Papa!

1223
01:28:47,432 --> 01:28:51,198
- 别担心 他没事儿的 - 我要爸爸！
- Don't worry. He's okay. - I want Papa!

1224
01:28:51,270 --> 01:28:52,737
没事儿的
It's okay.

1225
01:29:18,263 --> 01:29:21,596
我觉得那些庇护蟑螂的胡图族人
I say those Hutus who shelter the cockroaches

1226
01:29:21,667 --> 01:29:23,999
同蟑螂毫无差别
are the same as cockroaches.

1227
01:29:26,138 --> 01:29:28,003
- 他们是同类 - 太疯狂了
- They are all the same. - This is crazy.

1228
01:29:28,073 --> 01:29:32,134
他们应该有相同的命运 这里是RTLM（千丘广播电台）
Their fate should be the same. This is RTLM.

1229
01:29:43,188 --> 01:29:47,352
图西族叛军一定对征兵表示否认
The Tutsi cockroaches of the rebel army must be denied recruits.

1230
01:29:47,426 --> 01:29:51,021
来吧 胡图族人 坟墓尚有余位
Come on. good Hutus. The graves are not yet full.

1231
01:29:51,096 --> 01:29:53,963
- 谁愿意去填补空缺？ - 该死的电台
- Who will help us fill them? - That goddamn radio station.

1232
01:29:55,067 --> 01:29:58,332
好 是的 他们正去机场
Okay. Yeah, they are going to the airport.

1233
01:30:01,907 --> 01:30:05,934
锁定你的广播频率 我听到些紧急新闻
Stand by your radios. I am hearing some urgent news.

1234
01:30:07,145 --> 01:30:10,239
- 老板！拜托 快来！ - 现在不行 杜比
- Boss! Please, come quick! - Not now, Dube.

1235
01:30:10,315 --> 01:30:13,284
很重要！正在广播 你快来听
It is important! It is on the radio. You have to hear it.

1236
01:30:14,653 --> 01:30:17,918
我们收到非常重要消息 说有蟑螂
We have received reports of very important cockroaches

1237
01:30:17,990 --> 01:30:21,824
和叛徒试图逃离米勒・科林斯饭店
and traitors trying to escape from the Mille Collines Hotel.

1238
01:30:21,894 --> 01:30:23,418
收起你们的武器吧
Gather up your weapons.

1239
01:30:23,495 --> 01:30:26,658
锁定您的广播频率 我们会有后续报道
Stand by your radios. We will keep you informed.

1240
01:30:26,732 --> 01:30:28,347
他们正被偷运出国…
They are being smuggled away...

1241
01:30:28,347 --> 01:30:29,963
不 不！谁告诉他们的 杜比？
No, no! Who told them of this, Dube?

1242
01:30:30,035 --> 01:30:31,667
我看到格莱戈瓦了 先生
I saw Gregoire, sir. It is Gregoire.

1243
01:30:31,667 --> 01:30:33,300
一定是格莱戈瓦 我在大巴上看到了他
I saw him leaving in our bus.

1244
01:30:42,881 --> 01:30:45,372
拜托 先生 你要什么我都给你
Please, sir, I will give you whatever I have.

1245
01:30:45,450 --> 01:30:48,010
我要知道谁离开了饭店 而不是其他人
I say who leaves that hotel, and no one else.

1246
01:30:50,455 --> 01:30:53,356
比齐蒙戈将军 他们遭到了伏击
General Bizimungu, they are driving into an ambush.

1247
01:31:13,779 --> 01:31:14,939
慢点
Slow down.

1248
01:31:16,815 --> 01:31:18,407
别慌
Stay calm.

1249
01:31:19,017 --> 01:31:20,917
- 怎么回事？ - 车停了
- What is happening? - We're stopping.

1250
01:31:23,088 --> 01:31:25,318
你们车上藏了蟑螂
You have got cockroaches in these trucks.

1251
01:31:25,390 --> 01:31:27,756
没有 不是 车上都是联合国的人员
No, no. I've got U.N. personnel in these trucks.

1252
01:31:27,826 --> 01:31:30,056
我获准可以通过路障
I've got permission to go through these roadblocks.

1253
01:31:30,128 --> 01:31:31,794
我要搜查车厢 
I'm going to search these trucks.

1254
01:31:31,794 --> 01:31:33,461
你不能搜查这个车队
You are not going to search this convoy.

1255
01:31:35,100 --> 01:31:37,227
- 我要 - 掩护我
- I am. - Cover me.

1256
01:31:44,276 --> 01:31:45,766
到后面去
Go to the back.

1257
01:31:51,783 --> 01:31:55,412
别靠近车辆 别靠近车辆！马上离开！
Get away from that truck. Get away from that truck! Now!

1258
01:32:04,997 --> 01:32:07,124
退后！你们不能伤及这些人
Get back! You're not to hurt these people.

1259
01:32:08,700 --> 01:32:10,190
退后！退后！
Get back! Move back!

1260
01:32:10,869 --> 01:32:13,269
听着 我给你讲 你车上藏有蟑螂
Look, I told you, you've got cockroaches in your truck.

1261
01:32:13,338 --> 01:32:17,001
不 不 不 他们是联合国批准的政治难民
No, no, no. They're political refugees under U.N. sanction.

1262
01:32:20,612 --> 01:32:24,776
有消息称 我们自己的军中有胆小怕事之人
News has come to us that we have cowards in our own army

1263
01:32:24,850 --> 01:32:27,011
不让我们惩罚他们
who will not let us punish them.

1264
01:32:30,188 --> 01:32:31,177
不！
No!

1265
01:32:33,291 --> 01:32:35,282
你想从米勒・科林斯饭店带走蟑螂？
You're moving cockroaches from Mille Collines?

1266
01:32:35,360 --> 01:32:37,828
不 先生 不 先生 他们是政治难民
No, sir. No, sir, they're political refugees.

1267
01:32:37,896 --> 01:32:40,956
- 他们不能离开米勒・科林斯饭店 - 他们都不能离开
- They cannot leave Mille Collines. - They are not leaving.

1268
01:32:41,833 --> 01:32:42,857
阻止他！
Stop him!

1269
01:32:45,237 --> 01:32:46,602
你个混蛋！
You bastard!

1270
01:32:52,377 --> 01:32:53,435
你叫什么？
What's your name?

1271
01:32:53,512 --> 01:32:55,878
- 你叫什么名字？ - 我不知道…
- What's your name? - I can't think...

1272
01:32:56,681 --> 01:32:59,650
- 杀了他们！ - 所有人都离开这儿！走！
- Kill them! - Get everybody out of here! Move it!

1273
01:32:59,718 --> 01:33:02,551
你叫什么名字？叫什么名字？
What's your name? What's your name?

1274
01:33:03,155 --> 01:33:04,486
我们走！快开车！
Let's move! Drive!

1275
01:33:04,556 --> 01:33:06,319
走！出去！
Move! Get out!

1276
01:33:06,391 --> 01:33:07,881
出去 我开枪了！
Out, or I'll shoot!

1277
01:33:11,129 --> 01:33:12,118
出去！
Get out!

1278
01:33:15,901 --> 01:33:17,493
开车 开车！我们走！
Drive, drive! Let's go!

1279
01:33:18,437 --> 01:33:20,428
帮我们离开这儿
Help us get out of here.

1280
01:33:20,505 --> 01:33:22,268
清理路面！
Clear the street!

1281
01:33:31,917 --> 01:33:34,579
我又收到了消息 胡图族人
I am receiving more news. good Hutus.

1282
01:33:34,653 --> 01:33:38,487
我在车上发现了
I have learned that the traitor Rusesabagina's cockroaches

1283
01:33:38,557 --> 01:33:39,956
叛徒卢斯赛伯吉纳曾庇护的蟑螂
are on a truck.

1284
01:33:40,025 --> 01:33:42,255
他们的头值10,000法郎！
10.000 francs for their heads!

1285
01:33:44,529 --> 01:33:47,191
别动 给我你的衣服 快
Stay still. Give me your shirt, quickly.

1286
01:33:56,775 --> 01:33:58,766
快来 保罗 快来 快来！
Come on, Paul. Come on, come on!

1287
01:33:58,844 --> 01:34:01,870
快来 这儿 这儿 手给我 来
Come on, here, here. Give me your hand. Come on.

1288
01:34:04,416 --> 01:34:05,713
拜托 拜托
Please, please.

1289
01:34:05,784 --> 01:34:08,617
- 嘿 医生 叫个医生来！ - 你快点 拜托
- Hey, medic. Get a medic over here! - You need to hurry up, please.

1290
01:34:08,687 --> 01:34:10,416
来 快 快
Come, hurry, hurry.

1291
01:34:13,291 --> 01:34:15,725
- 我来帮你 - 来个人帮帮这个警卫好吗
- Let me help you. - Someone give this guard a hand, please.

1292
01:34:18,697 --> 01:34:20,187
噢 塔莎娜 我亲爱的
Oh, Tatiana, my darling.

1293
01:34:23,268 --> 01:34:25,463
- 我好担心你 - 别让车挡在路上！
- I was so worried about you. - Move that truck out of the way!

1294
01:34:25,537 --> 01:34:26,526
带他进去！
Get him inside!

1295
01:34:27,339 --> 01:34:29,500
塔莎娜 塔莎娜
Tatiana. Tatiana.

1296
01:34:30,842 --> 01:34:33,333
你扔下我不管 你扔下我不管
You left me. You left me.

1297
01:34:33,411 --> 01:34:35,504
这个拿回去 我不想要 我不想要
Take this. I don't want it. I don't want it.

1298
01:34:35,580 --> 01:34:38,378
你说你不会撇下我的 而你却扔下了我 你这个骗子！
You said you'd never leave me, and you left me. You are a liar!

1299
01:34:40,619 --> 01:34:42,746
抱歉 抱歉
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

1300
01:34:42,821 --> 01:34:44,618
- 很抱歉 - 爸爸 爸爸
- I'm sorry. - Papa, Papa.

1301
01:34:44,689 --> 01:34:47,590
- 爸爸 妈妈！ - 我爱你们
- Papa, Mama! - I love you.

1302
01:34:56,234 --> 01:34:58,998
我想让你们安全 你们所有人
I wanted you to be safe, all of you.

1303
01:34:59,871 --> 01:35:02,533
决定不是由你一个人说了算
That was not your decision to make.

1304
01:35:02,607 --> 01:35:06,043
我们应该一起决定 我们发过誓的
We make our decisions together. That was our promise.

1305
01:35:06,111 --> 01:35:07,806
你说得对
You're right.

1306
01:35:07,979 --> 01:35:09,913
你说得对
You're right.

1307
01:35:09,981 --> 01:35:12,882
当车开走的一瞬间 我理解
I knew that the minute the truck pulled away.

1308
01:35:12,951 --> 01:35:14,350
抱歉
I'm sorry.

1309
01:35:14,686 --> 01:35:15,880
来 再多点水
Come on, put some more water.

1310
01:35:15,954 --> 01:35:17,512
他们在干什么？
What are they doing?

1311
01:35:18,623 --> 01:35:20,147
杜比
Dube.

1312
01:35:20,926 --> 01:35:24,589
抱歉 先生 水阀被关了 我们只能用这个了
I'm sorry, sir. They shut down the water. This is all we have.

1313
01:35:31,136 --> 01:35:32,797
将军
General.

1314
01:35:32,871 --> 01:35:34,338
我的补给品呢？
Where are my supplies?

1315
01:35:35,173 --> 01:35:37,073
抱歉 先生 仓库都空了
I'm sorry, sir. The cellar is empty.

1316
01:35:37,142 --> 01:35:42,205
你一无所有 还打电话给我 求我帮你？
You have nothing, and yet you call me, begging me for help?

1317
01:35:42,280 --> 01:35:44,612
你知道为了保护这些蟑螂 我惹了多大麻烦？
Do you know the trouble I have protecting these cockroaches?

1318
01:35:44,683 --> 01:35:46,981
先生 我有房客们的钱
Sir, I have money from the guests.

1319
01:35:47,052 --> 01:35:48,986
卢旺达法郎！
Rwandan francs!

1320
01:35:49,955 --> 01:35:52,116
这些你只能拿去擦屁股
Those are only good for wiping your ass.

1321
01:35:53,692 --> 01:35:55,819
我不会再帮你了 保罗
There is nothing more I can do for you, Paul.

1322
01:35:55,894 --> 01:35:58,556
不会再给你警察 不会再给你保护
No more police, no more protection.

1323
01:35:59,931 --> 01:36:02,798
让联合国保护你吧
Let the U.N. take care of you.

1324
01:36:05,737 --> 01:36:07,466
开车 走！
Drive. Go!

1325
01:36:14,045 --> 01:36:16,172
对此比利时航空有什么措施？
What would Sabena make of this?

1326
01:36:23,989 --> 01:36:25,081
当心！
Watch out!

1327
01:36:31,062 --> 01:36:32,586
趴下 趴下！
Get down, get down!

1328
01:36:37,135 --> 01:36:39,399
受伤了吗？到外面去
Are you hurt? Go outside.

1329
01:36:39,471 --> 01:36:41,996
带着别动 这儿有碎玻璃 我来解决
Please stay still. There's glass here. I will get it out.

1330
01:36:42,073 --> 01:36:43,802
有人受伤吗 奥德特？
Is anyone hurt, Odette?

1331
01:36:43,875 --> 01:36:46,002
很多人被割伤、擦伤
Lots of cuts and bruises.

1332
01:36:52,484 --> 01:36:54,349
感谢上帝这只是储藏室
Thank God it was a storeroom.

1333
01:36:56,288 --> 01:36:59,223
在卢旺达 人道主义机构报道称
And in Rwanda. humanitarian agencies report

1334
01:36:59,291 --> 01:37:01,816
图西族叛军的快速增长
that a rapid advance by the Tutsi rebel army

1335
01:37:01,893 --> 01:37:05,761
让大批胡图族难民逃向刚果
has sparked a mass evacuation of Hutu refugees towards the Congo.

1336
01:37:05,830 --> 01:37:07,991
一名援助者描述说
One aid worker described it

1337
01:37:08,066 --> 01:37:11,092
这是近代史上最大的一次难民潮
as the largest refugee exodus in modern history.

1338
01:37:11,169 --> 01:37:12,864
反叛分子占领了半个城市
The rebels have taken half the city,

1339
01:37:12,937 --> 01:37:17,135
他们提出的条件 胡图族将军愿意接受
and they have proposed a deal the Hutu generals are willing to accept.

1340
01:37:18,043 --> 01:37:21,069
反叛分子决定用胡图族的囚犯作交换
The rebels will exchange their Hutu prisoners,

1341
01:37:21,146 --> 01:37:22,977
你们呢 所有的人
and you people, all of you,

1342
01:37:23,048 --> 01:37:26,415
将被转移到叛军后方的安全地带
will be able to move behind the rebel lines where it's safe.

1343
01:37:26,484 --> 01:37:28,543
部族民兵呢 他们怎么样？
The lnterhamwe, what about them?

1344
01:37:28,620 --> 01:37:31,953
- 没人能控制他们 - 他们现在要杀了我们所有人
- No one controls them. - This time they will kill us all.

1345
01:37:32,023 --> 01:37:34,423
如果呆在这儿 他们才会杀了我们所有人
They will kill us all if we stay here.

1346
01:37:35,093 --> 01:37:36,822
我们必须把握机会
We have to take the chance.

1347
01:37:37,762 --> 01:37:39,753
我们应该什么时候撤离？
What time should we be ready to leave?

1348
01:37:40,699 --> 01:37:42,792
我想两天后应该可以 保罗
I can put it together in two days, Paul.

1349
01:37:42,867 --> 01:37:44,129
两天？
Two days?

1350
01:37:44,969 --> 01:37:47,699
上校 我们不能在这儿呆上两天的时间
Colonel, there is no way that we can hold out for two days.

1351
01:37:47,772 --> 01:37:49,569
我一无所有了 无法贿赂他们
I have nothing left to bribe them with.

1352
01:37:51,109 --> 01:37:55,170
上校 两天后我们都会死的
Colonel, we will all be dead in two days.

1353
01:38:18,803 --> 01:38:21,966
黛安…让你妈妈睡吧
Diane...Iet your mother rest.

1354
01:38:22,040 --> 01:38:24,372
你也睡了 甜心 睡吧
You rest too, sweetheart. Go to sleep.

1355
01:38:33,218 --> 01:38:34,446
外交官饭店
Diplomat.

1356
01:38:36,454 --> 01:38:37,512
什么？
What?

1357
01:38:38,423 --> 01:38:40,357
我要去外交官饭店
I have to go to the Diplomat.

1358
01:38:50,668 --> 01:38:53,535
- 你要干什么？ - 我们得去外交官饭店
- What are you doing? - We have to go to the Diplomat.

1359
01:38:53,605 --> 01:38:56,130
- 去干什么？ - 你的东西 放在那儿
- To do what? - Your items, they are there.

1360
01:38:57,575 --> 01:39:00,066
让你的警察守住门好吗 先生？
Will you please put your policemen at the gate, sir?

1361
01:39:00,145 --> 01:39:03,046
不 我们先去看看你有什么给我
No. Let us see what you have to offer first.

1362
01:39:14,492 --> 01:39:16,653
噢 不 阿彻夫人
Oh, no. Madame Archer.

1363
01:39:34,512 --> 01:39:35,501
快走 快走！
Move, move!

1364
01:39:40,952 --> 01:39:42,283
- 掩护我们 - 是的 先生
- Cover us. - Yes, sir.

1365
01:39:42,353 --> 01:39:43,342
快！
Hurry!

1366
01:39:47,692 --> 01:39:48,989
快点 让我看
Come on, show me.

1367
01:39:58,203 --> 01:40:01,036
看这个 不错 对吧？
Look at this. Nice, yes?

1368
01:40:01,806 --> 01:40:03,137
还有这些
And here you are.

1369
01:40:09,948 --> 01:40:12,508
反叛分子越来越近了 对吗？
The rebels are getting closer, yes?

1370
01:40:13,384 --> 01:40:15,909
反叛分子能将此变为坟场
The rebels can have this graveyard.

1371
01:40:15,987 --> 01:40:18,319
我们下令所有人都离开这个城市
We have ordered everyone out of the city.

1372
01:40:21,059 --> 01:40:22,219
来
Here.

1373
01:40:23,328 --> 01:40:24,556
喝一口
Have a drink.

1374
01:40:31,336 --> 01:40:33,327
你知道苏格兰人怎么叫这个？
You know what the Scottish call it?

1375
01:40:33,404 --> 01:40:34,894
不知道
No.

1376
01:40:36,741 --> 01:40:40,142
Uisge beatha――生命之泉
Uisge beatha--water of life.

1377
01:40:46,351 --> 01:40:52,290
我去世界上最好的单一麦芽酿酒厂参观过
I went once on a tour of the finest single malt distillery in the world.

1378
01:40:53,157 --> 01:40:56,092
- 你去过苏格兰吗？ - 没有 先生
- Have you ever been to Scotland? - No, sir.

1379
01:40:57,228 --> 01:40:58,718
很不错的国家
Wonderful country.

1380
01:40:59,464 --> 01:41:01,056
能玩很棒的高尔夫球
Wonderful golf.

1381
01:41:02,300 --> 01:41:05,394
我不知道 我是否还能回去？
I wonder, will I ever go back?

1382
01:41:07,038 --> 01:41:08,300
你觉得呢？
What do you think?

1383
01:41:09,674 --> 01:41:10,834
不
No.

1384
01:41:12,443 --> 01:41:15,435
我希望我们都能接触到许许多多的东西 将军
I hope we all get to do a great many things, General.

1385
01:41:16,948 --> 01:41:18,506
请问我们可以走了吗 先生？
Can we go now, please, sir?

1386
01:41:20,251 --> 01:41:22,913
我要帮你个大忙 保罗
I am going to do you a great favor, Paul.

1387
01:41:23,021 --> 01:41:24,955
- 士兵 - 是 先生！
- Private. - Yes, sir!

1388
01:41:25,023 --> 01:41:28,220
小心装好 放在我吉普车上 守好
Pack those carefully, put them in my jeep, and guard them.

1389
01:41:28,993 --> 01:41:33,521
我要带你到吉塔拉马我们新司令部去
I am going to take you with us to our new headquarters in Gitarama.

1390
01:41:34,299 --> 01:41:36,392
我不想去吉塔拉马 先生
I do not want to go to Gitarama, sir.

1391
01:41:36,467 --> 01:41:39,129
呃 你不能回饭馆去
Well, you can't go back to the hotel.

1392
01:41:39,203 --> 01:41:41,034
疯狂的人正奔向那儿
The crazy men are on their way there now.

1393
01:41:41,105 --> 01:41:46,509
先生…将军 我们得回去 我要带走我的家人
Sir...General, we must go back so that I can get my family.

1394
01:41:46,578 --> 01:41:49,706
相信我 比在这儿境况好得多
Trust me, we are better off here.

1395
01:41:49,781 --> 01:41:54,650
将军 这是困难时期
General, these are difficult times.

1396
01:41:54,719 --> 01:41:56,516
我们需要相互帮助
We need to help one another.

1397
01:41:56,588 --> 01:41:59,921
我需要你帮我什么 保罗？
And what help can I get from you, Paul?

1398
01:41:59,991 --> 01:42:03,427
- 你是众人瞩目的人 先生 - 那又怎样？
- You are a marked man, sir. - How so?

1399
01:42:03,494 --> 01:42:04,394
你在名单上
You are on a list. 

1400
01:42:04,400 --> 01:42:07,294
美国人把你写在战犯的名单上
The Americans have you on their list as a war criminal.

1401
01:42:07,365 --> 01:42:10,357
保罗 我很讨厌也很厌倦你骗我
Paul, I am sick and tired of your lies.

1402
01:42:10,435 --> 01:42:13,199
你傻了吗 将军？
Are you stupid, General?

1403
01:42:13,271 --> 01:42:15,466
你觉得那些人会怎么做？
How do you think these people operate?

1404
01:42:15,540 --> 01:42:17,770
在这儿你胸前有五颗勋章
You sit here with five stars on your chest.

1405
01:42:17,770 --> 01:42:20,000
你想想是谁让你得到的？
 Who do you think they are coming after?

1406
01:42:24,616 --> 01:42:25,776
很好
Fine.

1407
01:42:27,185 --> 01:42:31,121
我们去吉塔拉马 你就会一直写在那个名单上
We will go to Gitarama, and you will stay on that list.

1408
01:42:31,189 --> 01:42:35,091
- 我没有从事任何战争犯罪 - 谁来评判呢？
- I committed no war crimes. - Who will tell them?

1409
01:42:35,159 --> 01:42:38,094
你要我来说 你是如何帮助饭店的人的
You need me to tell them how you helped at the hotel.

1410
01:42:38,162 --> 01:42:41,393
他们谴责你带来的不幸 他们说你领导了屠杀
They blame you for all their misfortunes. They say you led the massacres.

1411
01:42:41,466 --> 01:42:42,956
我没有领导屠杀！
I led no massacres!

1412
01:42:43,034 --> 01:42:44,968
你觉得他们会信你吗？
Do you think they're going to believe you?

1413
01:42:45,036 --> 01:42:46,560
你去告诉他们真相！
You will tell them the truth!

1414
01:42:46,638 --> 01:42:48,833
我绝不告诉他们 除非你帮我
I will tell them nothing unless you help me.

1415
01:42:50,675 --> 01:42:53,109
你要干什么 杀了我？
What are you going to do, shoot me?

1416
01:42:55,146 --> 01:42:56,477
杀了我啊
Shoot me.

1417
01:42:57,115 --> 01:42:59,242
拜托杀了我 上帝赐予我的
Please shoot me. It would be a blessing.

1418
01:42:59,317 --> 01:43:02,650
你杀了我的家人我会偿还的
I will pay you to shoot my family.

1419
01:43:03,655 --> 01:43:04,986
你不能伤害我
You cannot hurt me.

1420
01:43:05,056 --> 01:43:08,617
你去告诉他们 我什么都没干！
You will tell them that I did nothing!

1421
01:43:11,362 --> 01:43:14,229
我们走 就现在
We are leaving. Right now.

1422
01:43:23,074 --> 01:43:25,042
出来！
Get out!

1423
01:43:27,345 --> 01:43:29,404
别让人到门口去！
Get these people away from the gate!

1424
01:43:35,253 --> 01:43:37,312
停！停！
Stop it! Stop it!

1425
01:43:37,989 --> 01:43:39,320
离开饭店
Clear the hotel.

1426
01:43:40,091 --> 01:43:42,252
- 塔莎娜！ - 离开这儿！
- Tatiana! - Get out of here!

1427
01:43:42,326 --> 01:43:43,725
- 出去！ - 塔莎娜！
- Get out! - Tatiana!

1428
01:43:44,529 --> 01:43:45,791
出去！
Get out!

1429
01:43:47,165 --> 01:43:50,794
所有民兵都离开！出去！
All of the militia must leave now! Get out!

1430
01:44:12,390 --> 01:44:13,550
噢 不 不！
Oh, no, no!

1431
01:44:13,624 --> 01:44:15,114
闭嘴 蟑螂！蹲下！
Shut up, cockroach! Get down!

1432
01:44:17,628 --> 01:44:19,493
就是他 就是他！
That's him. That's him!

1433
01:44:20,631 --> 01:44:22,758
- 见鬼 - 经理在那儿！
- Shit. - That's the manager!

1434
01:44:22,834 --> 01:44:26,099
- 抓住他 抓住他！ - 我看到他了！我看到他了！
- Stop him. Stop him! - I got him! I got him!

1435
01:44:37,381 --> 01:44:39,406
呆着别动！
Stay where you are!

1436
01:44:56,400 --> 01:44:58,027
塔莎娜！
Tatiana!

1437
01:44:59,337 --> 01:45:01,066
塔莎娜！
Tatiana!

1438
01:45:07,044 --> 01:45:09,308
- 看到塔莎娜了吗？ - 没有 没看到塔莎娜
- Have you seen Tatiana? - No, I've not seen Tatiana.

1439
01:45:09,380 --> 01:45:11,871
- 保罗 怎么了？ - 我要去找我妻子！
- Paul, what is happening? - I have to find my wife!

1440
01:45:14,185 --> 01:45:15,311
塔莎娜！
Tatiana!

1441
01:45:19,323 --> 01:45:20,483
塔莎娜！
Tatiana!

1442
01:45:47,251 --> 01:45:49,014
他们走了 他们走了
They've gone. They've gone.

1443
01:45:51,355 --> 01:45:52,344
他们走了
They've gone.

1444
01:45:57,261 --> 01:45:59,252
你拿这个干什么？
What were you going to do with this?

1445
01:46:08,973 --> 01:46:10,907
我还以为你…
I thought you had...

1446
01:46:10,975 --> 01:46:12,772
我还以为你跳了
I thought you had jumped.

1447
01:46:24,956 --> 01:46:27,117
所有人都到车上去 拜托
Everyone on the trucks, please.

1448
01:46:27,191 --> 01:46:29,955
带上你们的行李 一家人呆在一起
Take your luggage. Families please stay together.

1449
01:46:30,027 --> 01:46:32,894
- 噢 拜托 - 大家尽快 拜托
- Oh, please. - As fast as you can, everyone. Please.

1450
01:46:32,964 --> 01:46:35,398
所有人都能上去
There's enough room for everyone.

1451
01:46:38,703 --> 01:46:40,568
希望有朝一日我们能再回来
I hope someday we will come back.

1452
01:46:41,806 --> 01:46:43,000
我们走
Let's move out.

1453
01:46:53,050 --> 01:46:55,143
她怎么了？
What is wrong with her?

1454
01:46:55,820 --> 01:46:57,913
她发了高烧
She has a very high fever.

1455
01:47:05,730 --> 01:47:08,198
我们要去哪儿 爸爸？
Where are we going, Daddy?

1456
01:47:08,266 --> 01:47:09,893
安全的地方
Someplace safe.

1457
01:48:07,692 --> 01:48:08,920
上帝
My God.

1458
01:48:31,315 --> 01:48:32,907
怎么了？
What's happening?

1459
01:48:57,708 --> 01:49:00,905
来 我们走 孩子们蹲下来 带孩子们走这边
Come on, let's go. Children on the ground. Bring the children this way.

1460
01:49:00,978 --> 01:49:03,242
让他们到后面去 让他们到后面去
Pass them back, pass them back.

1461
01:49:09,320 --> 01:49:12,483
别停 别停！直接开过去
Do not stop. Do not stop! Go right on through.

1462
01:49:24,869 --> 01:49:26,302
趴下！
Get down!

1463
01:49:29,006 --> 01:49:30,132
蹲下！
Stay down!

1464
01:49:53,664 --> 01:49:55,154
怎么了？
What's happening there?

1465
01:49:58,669 --> 01:50:02,161
是反叛分子 我们正通过前线
It's the rebels. We're crossing the front line.

1466
01:50:03,140 --> 01:50:05,904
没事儿了 我们安全了
It's okay. We're safe.

1467
01:50:05,976 --> 01:50:07,102
没事儿了
It's okay.

1468
01:50:07,178 --> 01:50:09,169
没事儿了 这儿安全了 安全了
It's okay, you are safe here. You are safe.

1469
01:50:09,246 --> 01:50:12,875
现在没事儿了 坐下来
It's okay now. Sit back down.

1470
01:50:14,652 --> 01:50:15,812
嗨
Hello.

1471
01:50:46,517 --> 01:50:48,348
多弄点水来
Get some more water.

1472
01:50:49,620 --> 01:50:52,612
医生说他严重脱水
The doctor says he is very dehydrated.

1473
01:50:52,690 --> 01:50:55,215
我们到了 来 下来吧
We made it. Come on, let's get down.

1474
01:50:56,560 --> 01:50:58,391
- 来 - 没事儿了
- Come on. - It is okay.

1475
01:50:58,462 --> 01:51:00,191
- 她病了 - 好的
- She is sick. - Okay.

1476
01:51:01,165 --> 01:51:02,632
是的 她病得很厉害 抱住她
Yeah, she's very sick. Take her.

1477
01:51:05,069 --> 01:51:09,403
保罗 车在营地的另一边
Paul, the buses are on the other side of camp.

1478
01:51:09,473 --> 01:51:11,839
他们要带我去坦桑尼亚
They'll take you to Tanzania.

1479
01:51:11,909 --> 01:51:15,709
那就去 保罗 因为我也不知道何时才会再有机会
Go now, Paul, 'cause I don't know when there'd be another opportunity.

1480
01:51:15,779 --> 01:51:17,110
- 谢谢 - 是的
- Thank you. - Yeah.

1481
01:51:17,181 --> 01:51:19,411
- 好运 - 谢谢
- Good luck. - Thank you.

1482
01:51:22,386 --> 01:51:24,377
- 感谢上帝 - 我们到了
- Thank God. - We made it.

1483
01:51:24,455 --> 01:51:27,015
拜托 拜托 都到了 对吧？
Please, please. We are here, yeah?

1484
01:51:27,091 --> 01:51:28,718
- 谢谢 保罗 - 我们成功了
- Thank you, Paul. - We have made it.

1485
01:51:28,792 --> 01:51:30,783
- 谢谢 - 是的 是的 来
- Thank you. - Yes, yes. Come.

1486
01:51:31,262 --> 01:51:32,251
经理先生
Mr. Manager.

1487
01:51:32,329 --> 01:51:34,729
- 我只是想谢谢你 - 当然 史蒂文
- I just want to thank you. - Of course, Steven.

1488
01:51:34,798 --> 01:51:35,890
康斯坦茨！
Constance!

1489
01:51:36,834 --> 01:51:39,598
感谢上帝你还活着！见到你真是太高兴了
Thank God you are alive! It's so good to see you.

1490
01:51:39,670 --> 01:51:42,161
你见过我哥哥和嫂子吗？
Have you seen my brother and his wife?

1491
01:51:42,239 --> 01:51:43,399
都没有
None of them.

1492
01:51:44,175 --> 01:51:46,666
有人见过这些人吗？你不认…
Has anyone seen these people? You don't recog--

1493
01:51:46,744 --> 01:51:49,076
妈妈 快来看
Mama, come see quick.

1494
01:51:49,146 --> 01:51:51,614
- 抱歉 抱歉 - 你在哪儿看到她们的？
- Excuse me, excuse me. - Can you see them anywhere?

1495
01:51:53,617 --> 01:51:55,209
这儿 妈妈 看
Here, Mama, look.

1496
01:51:55,286 --> 01:51:56,548
拜托
Please.

1497
01:51:58,189 --> 01:52:01,454
看到了吗 妈妈？是她们吗？
Do you see them, Mama? Is that them?

1498
01:52:02,159 --> 01:52:03,956
是她们吗 妈妈？
Is that them, Mama?

1499
01:52:05,296 --> 01:52:07,389
你们认识这些人吗？
Do you recognize these people?

1500
01:52:07,464 --> 01:52:10,592
这个小姑娘 她叫爱耐丝 这是卡琳
This little girl, she's Anais, and this is Carine.

1501
01:52:10,668 --> 01:52:12,158
认识吗？
Do you recognize them?

1502
01:52:13,904 --> 01:52:17,601
- 女士 见过这些姑娘吗？ - 不 没有 没见过
- Ma'am, have you seen these girls? - No, no, I haven't.

1503
01:52:17,675 --> 01:52:19,836
有人见过这些姑娘吗？
Have any of you seen these girls?

1504
01:52:22,279 --> 01:52:24,975
爱耐丝 那是我哥哥
Anais. And that's my brother.

1505
01:52:25,049 --> 01:52:27,040
所有人都上车！
Everybody on the buses!

1506
01:52:35,793 --> 01:52:37,818
这儿有感觉吗？
Can you feel anything when I touch here?

1507
01:52:37,895 --> 01:52:39,920
所有人都上车！
Everybody on the buses!

1508
01:52:39,997 --> 01:52:42,591
别挡在路上好吗？我们过不去了！
Can you move out of the way? We need some room here!

1509
01:52:42,666 --> 01:52:45,999
- 我们会发现姑娘们的 塔莎 会的 - 好的
- We'll find the girls, Tatsi. We will. - Okay.

1510
01:52:49,940 --> 01:52:51,567
布西？
Boussey?

1511
01:52:51,642 --> 01:52:52,973
真的是你
It's you.

1512
01:52:56,046 --> 01:52:57,536
哪儿找到这个孩子的？
Where'd you find this child?

1513
01:52:57,615 --> 01:52:59,947
刚从米勒・科林斯饭店来的车上下来的
They just arrived on trucks from the Mille Collines.

1514
01:53:02,152 --> 01:53:06,088
米勒・科林斯饭店的难民请上车了
All Mille Collines evacuees to the buses now. please.

1515
01:53:06,156 --> 01:53:08,147
- 噢 不 - 我们得快点了 拜托
- Oh, no. - We need to hurry up, please.

1516
01:53:14,531 --> 01:53:16,863
来 睡一会儿吧
Come on, get some sleep.

1517
01:53:18,068 --> 01:53:19,194
等等！
Wait!

1518
01:53:28,846 --> 01:53:30,677
停停 拜托！
Hold it, please!

1519
01:53:33,450 --> 01:53:35,145
- 塔莎娜！ - 是帕特！
- Tatiana! - It's Pat!

1520
01:53:35,219 --> 01:53:37,687
- 塔莎娜！ - 阿彻夫人！
- Tatiana! - Madame Archer!

1521
01:53:37,755 --> 01:53:40,485
停车！停车 停车！
Stop the bus! Stop the bus, stop the bus!

1522
01:53:40,557 --> 01:53:41,717
来 来 来
Come. Come, come.

1523
01:53:42,593 --> 01:53:44,288
拜托 等等我们
Please, wait for us.

1524
01:53:44,361 --> 01:53:47,194
阿彻夫人 我很担心 还以为…
Madame Archer. I was so worried. I thought...

1525
01:53:48,432 --> 01:53:50,366
见到你真得太高兴了
It's wonderful to see you.

1526
01:53:50,434 --> 01:53:51,867
快来
Come quickly.

1527
01:53:59,310 --> 01:54:01,676
- 卡琳？ - 爱耐丝？
- Carine? - Anais?

1528
01:54:01,745 --> 01:54:02,973
爱耐丝？
Anais?

1529
01:54:03,047 --> 01:54:05,743
等着 只要一分钟
Just wait. It's gonna be just a minute now.

1530
01:54:07,651 --> 01:54:10,085
爱耐丝？卡琳？
Anais? Carine?

1531
01:54:24,768 --> 01:54:26,759
噢 上帝！
Oh, my God!

1532
01:54:28,072 --> 01:54:30,097
噢 上帝！
Oh, my God!

1533
01:54:30,174 --> 01:54:32,108
来 来 来！
Come, come, come!

1534
01:54:35,646 --> 01:54:39,582
嗨 卡琳 爱耐丝 嗨 你好吗 甜心？
Hello, Carine. Anais, hello. How are you, sweetheart?

1535
01:54:41,919 --> 01:54:43,580
来见见表姐妹？
Do you see your cousins?

1536
01:54:51,428 --> 01:54:53,794
他们说没位置了
They said there wasn't any room.

1537
01:54:53,864 --> 01:54:55,525
